lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_axlttri: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ¬ ( ( A = B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsr> B ⟷ ¬ ( ( A = B ∨ B \<lsr> A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pre_axlttri)
   have S2: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟷ A \<lsr> B )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   have S3: "( B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( B \<ls> A ⟷ B \<lsr> A )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   from S3 have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( B \<ls> A ⟷ B \<lsr> A )" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S4 have S5: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A = B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ⟷   
 ( A = B ∨ B \<lsr> A ) )" by (rule MMI_orbi2d)
   from S5 have S6: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ¬ ( ( A = B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ) ⟷   
 ¬ ( ( A = B ∨ B \<lsr> A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_negbid)
   from S1 S2 S6 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ¬ ( ( A = B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_3bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_axlttrn: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsr> B ∧ B \<lsr> C ) ⟶ A \<lsr> C )" by (rule MMI_pre_axlttrn)
   have S2: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟷ A \<lsr> B )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   from S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ A \<lsr> B )" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S4: "( B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( B \<ls> C ⟷ B \<lsr> C )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   from S4 have S5: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<ls> C ⟷ B \<lsr> C )" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S3 S5 have S6: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟷   
 ( A \<lsr> B ∧ B \<lsr> C ) )" by (rule MMI_anbi12d)
   have S7: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> C ⟷ A \<lsr> C )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   from S7 have S8: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> C ⟷ A \<lsr> C )" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   from S1 S6 S8 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_3imtr4d)
qed

(***************231-235********************************)

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_axltadd: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ( C \<ca> A ) \<ls> ( C \<ca> B ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsr> B ⟶ ( C \<ca> A ) \<lsr> ( C \<ca> B ) )" by (rule MMI_pre_axltadd)
   have S2: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟷ A \<lsr> B )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   from S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ A \<lsr> B )" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S4: "( ( C \<ca> A ) ∈ ℝ ∧ ( C \<ca> B ) ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( C \<ca> A ) \<ls> ( C \<ca> B ) ⟷   
 ( C \<ca> A ) \<lsr> ( C \<ca> B ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   have S5: "( C ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( C \<ca> A ) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axaddrcl)
   have S6: "( C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( C \<ca> B ) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axaddrcl)
   from S4 S5 S6 have S7: "( ( C ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ ( C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶   
 ( ( C \<ca> A ) \<ls> ( C \<ca> B ) ⟷   
 ( C \<ca> A ) \<lsr> ( C \<ca> B ) )" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S7 have S8: "( C ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( C \<ca> A ) \<ls> ( C \<ca> B ) ⟷   
 ( C \<ca> A ) \<lsr> ( C \<ca> B ) )" by (rule MMI_3impdi)
   from S8 have S9: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( C \<ca> A ) \<ls> ( C \<ca> B ) ⟷   
 ( C \<ca> A ) \<lsr> ( C \<ca> B ) )" by (rule MMI_3coml)
   from S1 S3 S9 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ( C \<ca> A ) \<ls> ( C \<ca> B ) )" by (rule MMI_3imtr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_axmulgt0: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ) ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> ( A ⋅ B ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( 𝟬 \<lsr> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsr> B ) ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsr> ( A ⋅ B ) )" by (rule MMI_pre_axmulgt0)
   have S2: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S3: "( 𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsr> A )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ ( 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsr> A )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
   have S5: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S6: "( 𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsr> B )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   from S5 S6 have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ ( 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsr> B )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
   from S4 S7 have S8: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ) ⟷   
 ( 𝟬 \<lsr> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsr> B ) )" by (rule MMI_bi2anan9)
   have S9: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A ⋅ B ) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   have S10: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S11: "( 𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ ( A ⋅ B ) ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( 𝟬 \<ls> ( A ⋅ B ) ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsr> ( A ⋅ B ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
   from S10 S11 have S12: "( A ⋅ B ) ∈ ℝ ⟶   
 ( 𝟬 \<ls> ( A ⋅ B ) ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsr> ( A ⋅ B ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
   from S9 S12 have S13: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( 𝟬 \<ls> ( A ⋅ B ) ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsr> ( A ⋅ B ) )" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S1 S8 S13 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ) ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> ( A ⋅ B ) )" by (rule MMI_3imtr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_axsup: 
   shows "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 0 ∧ ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<ls> x ) ) ⟶   
 ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ) ∧ 
  ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ) ) ) )"
proof -
  have S1: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 0 ∧ ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<lsr> x ) ) ⟶   
    ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) ∧ 
    ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) ) ) )" 
    by (rule MMI_pre_axsup)
  from S1 have S2: 
    "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 0 ) ∧ ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<lsr> x ) ) ⟶   
    ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) ∧ 
    ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) ) ) )" 
    by (rule MMI_3expa)
  from S2 have S3: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 0 ) ⟶   
    ( ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<lsr> x ) ⟶   
    ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) ∧ 
    ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) ) ) ) )" 
    by (rule MMI_ex)
  { fix x
    { fix y
      have S4: "( y ∈ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( y \<ls> x ⟷ y \<lsr> x )" 
	by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
      have S5: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ y ∈ A ) ⟶ y ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_ssel2)
      from S4 S5 have S6: "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ y ∈ A ) ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	( y \<ls> x ⟷ y \<lsr> x ) )" by (rule MMI_sylan)
      from S6 have "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ A ) ⟶   
	( y \<ls> x ⟷ y \<lsr> x ) )" by (rule MMI_an1rs)
    } then have S7: "∀y. ( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ A ) ⟶   
	( y \<ls> x ⟷ y \<lsr> x ) )" by simp
    from S7 have  "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
      ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . y \<ls> x ) ⟷   
      ( ∀ y ∈ A . y \<lsr> x ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ralbidva)
  } then have S8: "∀ x. ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
      ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . y \<ls> x ) ⟷   
      ( ∀ y ∈ A . y \<lsr> x ) ) )" by simp
    from S8 have S9: "( A ⊆ ℝ ⟶   
      ( ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<ls> x ) ⟷   
      ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<lsr> x ) ) )" by (rule MMI_rexbidva)
   from S9 have S10: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 0 ) ⟶   
 ( ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<ls> x ) ⟷   
 ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<lsr> x ) ) )" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   { fix x
     { fix y 
       have S11: "( x ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( x \<ls> y ⟷ x \<lsr> y )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
       from S11 have S12: "( y ∈ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( x \<ls> y ⟷ x \<lsr> y )" 
	 by (rule MMI_ancoms)
       have S13: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ y ∈ A ) ⟶ y ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_ssel2)
       from S12 S13 have S14: "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ y ∈ A ) ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	 ( x \<ls> y ⟷ x \<lsr> y ) )" by (rule MMI_sylan)
       from S14 have S15: "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ A ) ⟶   
	 ( x \<ls> y ⟷ x \<lsr> y ) )" by (rule MMI_an1rs)
       from S15 have  "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ A ) ⟶   
	 ( ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ⟷ ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) )" by (rule MMI_negbid)
     } then have S16:  "∀ y. ( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ A ) ⟶   
	 ( ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ⟷ ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) )" by simp
     from S16 have S17: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
       ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ) ⟷   
       ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ralbidva)
     { fix y
       have S18: "( y ∈ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( y \<ls> x ⟷ y \<lsr> x )" 
	 by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
       from S18 have S19: "( x ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( y \<ls> x ⟷ y \<lsr> x )" 
	 by (rule MMI_ancoms)
       from S19 have S20: "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	 ( y \<ls> x ⟷ y \<lsr> x ) )" by (rule MMI_adantll)
       { fix z
	 have S21: "( y ∈ ℝ ∧ z ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( y \<ls> z ⟷ y \<lsr> z )" by (rule MMI_ltxrltt)
	 from S21 have S22: "( z ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( y \<ls> z ⟷ y \<lsr> z )" 
	   by (rule MMI_ancoms)
	 have S23: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ z ∈ A ) ⟶ z ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_ssel2)
	 from S22 S23 have S24: "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ z ∈ A ) ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	   ( y \<ls> z ⟷ y \<lsr> z ) )" by (rule MMI_sylan)
	 from S24 have S25: "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ∧ z ∈ A ) ⟶   
	   ( y \<ls> z ⟷ y \<lsr> z ) )" by (rule MMI_an1rs)
       } then have S25: "∀z. ( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ∧ z ∈ A ) ⟶   
	   ( y \<ls> z ⟷ y \<lsr> z ) )" by simp
	 from S25 have S26: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	 ( ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ⟷   
	 ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) )" by (rule MMI_rexbidva)
	 from S26 have S27: "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	   ( ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ⟷   
	   ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) )" by (rule MMI_adantlr)
	 from S20 S27 have  "( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	   ( ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ⟷   
	   ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
       } then have S28: "∀ y. ( ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	   ( ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ⟷   
	   ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) )" by simp
       from S28 have S29: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
     ( ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ) ⟷   
	 ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) ) )" 
	 by (rule MMI_ralbidva)
       from S17 S29 have  "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	 ( ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ) ∧ 
	 ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ) ) ⟷   
	 ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) ∧ 
	 ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) ) ) )" 
	 by (rule MMI_anbi12d)
     } then have S30: "∀ x. ( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ x ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
	 ( ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ) ∧ 
	 ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ) ) ⟷   
	 ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) ∧ 
	 ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) ) ) )" 
       by simp
     from S30 have S31: "( A ⊆ ℝ ⟶   
       ( ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ) ∧ 
       ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ) ) ) ⟷   
       ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) ∧ 
       ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) ) ) ) )" 
       by (rule MMI_rexbidva)
     from S31 have S32: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 0 ) ⟶   
	 ( ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ) ∧ 
       ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ) ) ) ⟷   
	 ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<lsr> y ) ) ∧ 
       ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<lsr> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<lsr> z ) ) ) ) ) ) )" 
       by (rule MMI_adantr)
       from S3 S10 S32 have S33: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 0 ) ⟶   
	 ( ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<ls> x ) ⟶   
	 ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ) ∧ 
	 ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ) ) ) ) )" 
	 by (rule MMI_3imtr4d)
       from S33 show 
	 "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 0 ∧ ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ∀ y ∈ A . y \<ls> x ) ) ⟶   
	 ( ∃ x ∈ ℝ . ( ( ∀ y ∈ A . ¬ ( x \<ls> y ) ) ∧ 
	 ( ∀ y ∈ ℝ . ( y \<ls> x ⟶ ( ∃ z ∈ A . y \<ls> z ) ) ) ) ) )" 
	 by (rule MMI_3impia)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lenltt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ B ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_xrlenltt)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_rexrt)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_rexrt)
   from S1 S2 S3 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltnlet: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ¬ ( B \<lsq> A ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> A ⟷ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   from S1 have S2: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> A ⟷ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S2 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ¬ ( B \<lsq> A ) )" by (rule MMI_con2bid)
qed

(**********236*********************)

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltso: 
   shows "\<cltrrset> Orders ℝ"
proof -
  { fix x y z
    have S1: "( x ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
      ( x \<ls> y ⟷ ¬ ( ( x = y ∨ y \<ls> x ) ) )" by (rule MMI_axlttri)
    from S1 have S2: "( x ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ∧ z ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
      ( x \<ls> y ⟷ ¬ ( ( x = y ∨ y \<ls> x ) ) )" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
    have S3: "( x ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ∧ z ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
      ( ( x \<ls> y ∧ y \<ls> z ) ⟶ x \<ls> z )" by (rule MMI_axlttrn)
    from S2 S3 have "( x ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ∧ z ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
      ( ( x \<ls> y ⟷ ¬ ( ( x = y ∨ y \<ls> x ) ) ) ∧ 
      ( ( x \<ls> y ∧ y \<ls> z ) ⟶ x \<ls> z ) )" by (rule MMI_jca)
    then have 
      "( x ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ∧ z ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
      ( ( ⟨x, y⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ⟷ ¬ ( ( x = y ∨ ⟨y,x⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ) ) ) ∧ 
      ( ( ⟨x,y⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ∧ ⟨y,z⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ) ⟶ ⟨x, z⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ) )"
      using cltrr_def by simp
  } then have S4: "∀x y z. ( x ∈ ℝ ∧ y ∈ ℝ ∧ z ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
      ( ( ⟨x, y⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ⟷ ¬ ( ( x = y ∨ ⟨y,x⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ) ) ) ∧ 
      ( ( ⟨x,y⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ∧ ⟨y,z⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ) ⟶ ⟨x, z⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ) )"
    by auto
  from S4 show "\<cltrrset> Orders ℝ" by (rule MMI_so)
qed

(*********237-240************************)

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lttri2t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ¬ ( A = B ) ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cltrrset> Orders ℝ" by (rule MMI_ltso)
   have "( \<cltrrset> Orders ℝ ∧ ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶   
     ( A = B ⟷ ¬ ( ( ⟨A, B⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ∨ ⟨B,A ⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset>) ) )"
     by (rule MMI_sotrieq)
   then have S2: "( \<cltrrset> Orders ℝ ∧ ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶   
     ( A = B ⟷ ¬ ( ( A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ) )" using cltrr_def
     by simp
   from S1 S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
     ( A = B ⟷ ¬ ( ( A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
   from S3 have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
     ( ¬ ( ( A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ) ⟷ A = B )" by (rule MMI_bicomd)
   from S4 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
     ( ¬ ( A = B ) ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_con1bid)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lttri3t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A =   
 B ⟷ ( ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ∧ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ) )"
proof -
  have S1: "\<cltrrset> Orders ℝ" by (rule MMI_ltso)
  have "( \<cltrrset> Orders ℝ ∧ ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶   
    ( A = B ⟷ ( ¬ ( ⟨A, B⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ) ∧ ¬ ( ⟨B,A⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> ) ) )" 
    by (rule MMI_sotrieq2)
  then have S2: "( \<cltrrset> Orders ℝ ∧ ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶   
    ( A = B ⟷ ( ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ∧ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ) )"  using cltrr_def
    by simp
  from S1 S2 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
    ( A = B ⟷ ( ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ∧ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltnet: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ¬ ( A = B ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ¬ ( A = B ) ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_lttri2t)
   have S2: "A \<ls> B ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_orc)
   from S1 S2 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ¬ ( A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_syl5bir)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_letri3t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟷ ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> A ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A =   
 B ⟷ ( ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ∧ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_lttri3t)
   have S2: "( ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ∧ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ) ⟷   
 ( ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ∧ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_ancom)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A =   
 B ⟷ ( ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ∧ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_syl6bbr)
   have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   have S5: "( B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> A ⟷ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   from S5 have S6: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> A ⟷ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S4 S6 have S7: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> A ) ⟷   
 ( ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ∧ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_anbi12d)
   from S3 S7 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟷ ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> A ) )" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
qed

(************** 240-250********************************)

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_leloet: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   have S2: "( B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<ls> A ⟷ ¬ ( ( B = A ∨ A \<ls> B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_axlttri)
   from S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<ls> A ⟷ ¬ ( ( B = A ∨ A \<ls> B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S3 have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( B = A ∨ A \<ls> B ) ⟷ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_con2bid)
   have S5: "B = A ⟷ A = B" by (rule MMI_eqcom)
   from S5 have S6: "( B = A ∨ A \<ls> B ) ⟷ ( A = B ∨ A \<ls> B )" by (rule MMI_orbi1i)
   have S7: "( A = B ∨ A \<ls> B ) ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B )" by (rule MMI_orcom)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "( B = A ∨ A \<ls> B ) ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B )" by (rule MMI_bitr)
   from S4 S8 have S9: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_syl5rbbr)
   from S1 S9 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_eqleltt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟷ ( A \<lsq> B ∧ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟷ ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> A ) )" by (rule MMI_letri3t)
   have S2: "( B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> A ⟷ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   from S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> A ⟷ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S3 have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> A ) ⟷   
 ( A \<lsq> B ∧ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   from S1 S4 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟷ ( A \<lsq> B ∧ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltlet: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   have S2: "A \<ls> B ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B )" by (rule MMI_orc)
   from S1 S2 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B )" by (rule MMI_syl5bir)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_leltnet: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ¬ ( A = B ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A =   
 B ⟷ ( ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ∧ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_lttri3t)
   have S2: "( ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ∧ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ) ⟶   
 ¬ ( A \<ls> B )" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_syl6bi)
   from S3 have S4: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S5: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   from S5 have S6: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B )" by (rule MMI_biimpa)
   from S6 have S7: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) ⟶ A = B )" by (rule MMI_ord)
   from S4 S7 have S8: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟷ ¬ ( A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_impbid)
   from S8 have S9: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ¬ ( A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_con2bid)
   from S9 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ¬ ( A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_3impa)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltlent: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ( A \<lsq> B ∧ ¬ ( A = B ) ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B )" by (rule MMI_ltlet)
   have S2: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ¬ ( A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_ltnet)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ( A \<lsq> B ∧ ¬ ( A = B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_jcad)
   have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   have S5: "A \<ls> B ⟶ ( ¬ ( A = B ) ⟶ A \<ls> B )" by (rule MMI_ax_1)
   have S6: "A = B ⟶ ( ¬ ( A = B ) ⟶ A \<ls> B )" by (rule MMI_pm2_24)
   from S5 S6 have S7: "( A \<ls> B ∨ A =   
 B ) ⟶ ( ¬ ( A = B ) ⟶ A \<ls> B )" by (rule MMI_jaoi)
   from S4 S7 have S8: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟶ ( ¬ ( A = B ) ⟶ A \<ls> B ) )" by (rule MMI_syl6bi)
   from S8 have S9: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ ¬ ( A = B ) ) ⟶ A \<ls> B )" by (rule MMI_imp3a)
   from S3 S9 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ( A \<lsq> B ∧ ¬ ( A = B ) ) )" by (rule MMI_impbid)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lelttrt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   from S1 have S2: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) )" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_axlttrn)
   from S3 have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ( B \<ls> C ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_exp3a)
   have S5: "A = B ⟶ ( A \<ls> C ⟷ B \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S5 have S6: "A = B ⟶ ( B \<ls> C ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_biimprd)
   from S6 have S7: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A = B ⟶ ( B \<ls> C ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_a1i)
   from S4 S7 have S8: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ) ⟶   
 ( B \<ls> C ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_jaod)
   from S2 S8 have S9: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟶ ( B \<ls> C ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_sylbid)
   from S9 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_imp3a)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltletrt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<lsq> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )"
proof -
   have S1: "( B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> C ⟷ ( B \<ls> C ∨ B = C ) )" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   from S1 have S2: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> C ⟷ ( B \<ls> C ∨ B = C ) )" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_axlttrn)
   from S3 have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ( B \<ls> C ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_exp3a)
   from S4 have S5: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<ls> C ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_com23)
   have S6: "B = C ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S6 have S7: "B = C ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_biimpd)
   from S7 have S8: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B = C ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_a1i)
   from S5 S8 have S9: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( B \<ls> C ∨ B = C ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_jaod)
   from S2 S9 have S10: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> C ⟶ ( A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_sylbid)
   from S10 have S11: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ( B \<lsq> C ⟶ A \<ls> C ) )" by (rule MMI_com23)
   from S11 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<lsq> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_imp3a)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_letrt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> C ) ⟶ A \<lsq> C )"
proof -
   have S1: "( B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> C ⟷ ( B \<ls> C ∨ B = C ) )" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   from S1 have S2: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> C ⟷ ( B \<ls> C ∨ B = C ) )" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S2 have S3: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> C ⟷ ( B \<ls> C ∨ B = C ) )" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_lelttrt)
   have S5: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> C ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_ltlet)
   from S5 have S6: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> C ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   from S4 S6 have S7: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_syld)
   from S7 have S8: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟶ ( B \<ls> C ⟶ A \<lsq> C ) )" by (rule MMI_exp3a)
   from S8 have S9: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( B \<ls> C ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_imp)
   have S10: "B = C ⟶ ( A \<lsq> B ⟷ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S10 have S11: "A \<lsq> B ⟶ ( B = C ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_biimpcd)
   from S11 have S12: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( B = C ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   from S9 S12 have S13: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( ( B \<ls> C ∨ B = C ) ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_jaod)
   from S3 S13 have S14: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsq> B ) ⟶   
 ( B \<lsq> C ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_sylbid)
   from S14 have S15: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> B ⟶ ( B \<lsq> C ⟶ A \<lsq> C ) )" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S15 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> C ) ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_imp3a)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_letrd: assumes A1: "φ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "φ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "φ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" and
    A4: "φ ⟶ A \<lsq> B" and
    A5: "φ ⟶ B \<lsq> C"   
   shows "φ ⟶ A \<lsq> C"
proof -
   from A4 have S1: "φ ⟶ A \<lsq> B".
   from A5 have S2: "φ ⟶ B \<lsq> C".
   have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> C ) ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" by (rule MMI_letrt)
   from A1 have S4: "φ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S5: "φ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S6: "φ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ".
   from S3 S4 S5 S6 have S7: "φ ⟶ ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<lsq> C ) ⟶ A \<lsq> C )" 
     by (rule MMI_syl3anc)
   from S1 S2 S7 show "φ ⟶ A \<lsq> C" by (rule MMI_mp2and)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lelttrd: assumes A1: "φ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "φ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "φ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" and
    A4: "φ ⟶ A \<lsq> B" and
    A5: "φ ⟶ B \<ls> C"   
   shows "φ ⟶ A \<ls> C"
proof -
   from A4 have S1: "φ ⟶ A \<lsq> B".
   from A5 have S2: "φ ⟶ B \<ls> C".
   have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )" by (rule MMI_lelttrt)
   from A1 have S4: "φ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S5: "φ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S6: "φ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ".
   from S3 S4 S5 S6 have S7: "φ ⟶ ( ( A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> C ) ⟶ A \<ls> C )" 
     by (rule MMI_syl3anc)
   from S1 S2 S7 show "φ ⟶ A \<ls> C" by (rule MMI_mp2and)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltnrt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cltrrset> Orders ℝ" by (rule MMI_ltso)
   have "( \<cltrrset> Orders ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ¬ ( ⟨A,A⟩ ∈ \<cltrrset> )" 
     by (rule MMI_sonr)
   then have S2: "( \<cltrrset> Orders ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )" 
     using cltrr_def by simp
   from S1 S2 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_leidt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<lsq> A"
proof -
   have S1: "A = A" by (rule MMI_eqid)
   from S1 have S2: "¬ ( A \<ls> A ) ⟶ A = A" by (rule MMI_a1i)
   from S2 have S3: "A \<ls> A ∨ A = A" by (rule MMI_orri)
   have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> A ⟷ ( A \<ls> A ∨ A = A ) )" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶ A \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_mpbiri)
   from S5 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_anidms)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltnsymt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟷ ¬ ( ( A = B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_axlttri)
   have S2: "¬ ( ( A = B ∨ B \<ls> A ) ) ⟶ ¬ ( B \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_pm2_46)
   from S1 S2 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_syl6bi)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltnsym2t: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ¬ ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<ls> A ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> B ⟶ ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_ltnsymt)
   have S2: "( A \<ls> B ⟶   
 ¬ ( B \<ls> A ) ) ⟷   
 ¬ ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_imnan)
   from S1 S2 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ¬ ( ( A \<ls> B ∧ B \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_sylib)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_elxr: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟷ ( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A = \<cpnf> ∨ A = \<cmnf> )"
proof -
   have S1: "ℝ⇧* = ( ℝ ∪ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } )" by (rule MMI_df_xr)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟷ A ∈ ( ℝ ∪ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } )" by (rule MMI_eleq2i)
   have S3: "A ∈ ( ℝ ∪ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ⟷   
 ( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } )" by (rule MMI_elun)
   have S4: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_pnfxr)
   from S4 have S5: "\<cpnf> isASet" by (rule MMI_elisseti)
   have S6: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_mnfxr)
   from S6 have S7: "\<cmnf> isASet" by (rule MMI_elisseti)
   from S5 S7 have S8: "A ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ⟷ ( A = \<cpnf> ∨ A = \<cmnf> )"
     by (rule MMI_elpr2)
   from S8 have S9: "( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ⟷   
 ( A ∈ ℝ ∨ ( A = \<cpnf> ∨ A = \<cmnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_orbi2i)
   have S10: "( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A =   
 \<cpnf> ∨ A =   
 \<cmnf> ) ⟷ ( A ∈ ℝ ∨ ( A = \<cpnf> ∨ A = \<cmnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_3orass)
   from S9 S10 have S11: "( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ⟷   
 ( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A = \<cpnf> ∨ A = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_bitr4)
   from S2 S3 S11 show "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟷ ( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A = \<cpnf> ∨ A = \<cmnf> )" 
     by (rule MMI_3bitr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_pnfnemnf: 
   shows "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf>"
proof -
   have S1: "¬ ( ℂ ∈ ℂ )" by (rule MMI_eirr)
   have S2: "ℂ isASet" by (rule MMI_axcnex)
   from S2 have S3: "ℂ ∈ { ℂ }" by (rule MMI_snid)
   have S4: "ℂ = { ℂ } ⟶ ( ℂ ∈ ℂ ⟷ ℂ ∈ { ℂ } )" by (rule MMI_eleq2)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "ℂ = { ℂ } ⟶ ℂ ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_mpbiri)
   from S1 S5 have S6: "¬ ( ℂ = { ℂ } )" by (rule MMI_mto)
   have S7: "\<cpnf> = ℂ" by (rule MMI_df_pnf)
   have S8: "\<cmnf> = { ℂ }" by (rule MMI_df_mnf)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "\<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ⟷ ℂ = { ℂ }" by (rule MMI_eqeq12i)
   from S6 S9 have S10: "¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_mtbir)
   have S11: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S10 S11 show "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_mpbir)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_renepnft: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ≠ \<cpnf>"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cpnf> ∉ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pnfnre)
   have S2: "\<cpnf> ∉ ℝ ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_df_nel)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ ¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶ ¬ ( A = \<cpnf> )" 
     by (rule MMI_nelneq)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ ¬ ( A = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_mpan2)
   have S6: "A ≠ \<cpnf> ⟷ ¬ ( A = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S5 S6 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ≠ \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_sylibr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_renemnft: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ≠ \<cmnf>"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cmnf> ∉ ℝ" by (rule MMI_minfnre)
   have S2: "\<cmnf> ∉ ℝ ⟷ ¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_df_nel)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   have S4: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ ¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶ ¬ ( A = \<cmnf> )" 
     by (rule MMI_nelneq)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ ¬ ( A = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_mpan2)
   have S6: "A ≠ \<cmnf> ⟷ ¬ ( A = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S5 S6 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ≠ \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_sylibr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_renfdisj: 
   shows "( ℝ ∩ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) = 0"
proof -
   have S1: "{ \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } = ( { \<cpnf> } ∪ { \<cmnf> } )" by (rule MMI_df_pr)
   from S1 have S2: "( ℝ ∩ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) =   
 ( ℝ ∩ ( { \<cpnf> } ∪ { \<cmnf> } ) )" by (rule MMI_ineq2i)
   have S3: "\<cpnf> = \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_eqid)
   have S4: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ⟶ \<cpnf> ≠ \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_renepnft)
   have S5: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cpnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ⟶ ¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_sylib)
   from S3 S6 have S7: "¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_mt2)
   have S8: "( ℝ ∩ { \<cpnf> } ) = 0 ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_disjsn)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "( ℝ ∩ { \<cpnf> } ) = 0" by (rule MMI_mpbir)
   have S10: "\<cmnf> = \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_eqid)
   have S11: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ⟶ \<cmnf> ≠ \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_renemnft)
   have S12: "\<cmnf> ≠ \<cmnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S11 S12 have S13: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ⟶ ¬ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_sylib)
   from S10 S13 have S14: "¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_mt2)
   have S15: "( ℝ ∩ { \<cmnf> } ) = 0 ⟷ ¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_disjsn)
   from S14 S15 have S16: "( ℝ ∩ { \<cmnf> } ) = 0" by (rule MMI_mpbir)
   from S9 S16 have S17: "( ℝ ∩ { \<cpnf> } ) = 0 ∧ ( ℝ ∩ { \<cmnf> } ) = 0" by (rule MMI_pm3_2i)
   have S18: "( ( ℝ ∩ { \<cpnf> } ) =   
 0 ∧ ( ℝ ∩ { \<cmnf> } ) =   
 0 ) ⟷ ( ℝ ∩ ( { \<cpnf> } ∪ { \<cmnf> } ) ) = 0" by (rule MMI_undisj2)
   from S17 S18 have S19: "( ℝ ∩ ( { \<cpnf> } ∪ { \<cmnf> } ) ) = 0" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S2 S19 show "( ℝ ∩ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) = 0" by (rule MMI_eqtr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ssxr: 
   shows "( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ( A ⊆ ℝ ∨ \<cpnf> ∈ A ∨ \<cmnf> ∈ A ) )"
proof -
   have S1: "( ( A ∩ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) =   
 0 ⟶   
 ( A ⊆ ( { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ∪ ℝ ) ⟷ A ⊆ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_disjssun)
   have S2: "ℝ⇧* = ( ℝ ∪ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } )" by (rule MMI_df_xr)
   have S3: "( ℝ ∪ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) = ( { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ∪ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_uncom)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "ℝ⇧* = ( { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ∪ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_eqtr)
   from S4 have S5: "( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟷ A ⊆ ( { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ∪ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_sseq2i)
   from S1 S5 have S6: "( ( A ∩ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) =   
 0 ⟶ ( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟷ A ⊆ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_syl5bb)
   from S6 have S7: "( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( ( A ∩ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) = 0 ⟶ A ⊆ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_biimpcd)
   have S8: "( A ∩ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) =   
 0 ⟷ ( ∀ x ∈ A . ¬ ( x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) )" by (rule MMI_disj)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( ( ∀ x ∈ A . ¬ ( x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ) ⟶   
 A ⊆ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_syl5ibr)
   from S9 have S10: "( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( ¬ ( A ⊆ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ¬ ( ( ∀ x ∈ A . ¬ ( x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_con3d)
   have S11: "( ∃ x ∈ A . x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ⟷   
     ¬ ( ( ∀ x ∈ A . ¬ ( x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ) )" by (rule MMI_dfrex2)
   { fix x
     have S12: "x isASet" by (rule MMI_visset)
     from S12 have 
       "x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ⟷ ( x = \<cpnf> ∨ x = \<cmnf> )" 
       by (rule MMI_elpr)
   } then have S13: 
       "∀x. x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ⟷ ( x = \<cpnf> ∨ x = \<cmnf> )"  
     by simp
   from S13 have S14: "( ∃ x ∈ A . x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ⟷   
     ( ∃ x ∈ A . ( x = \<cpnf> ∨ x = \<cmnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_rexbii)
   from S11 S14 have S15: 
     "¬ ( ( ∀ x ∈ A . ¬ ( x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ) ) ⟷   
     ( ∃ x ∈ A . ( x = \<cpnf> ∨ x = \<cmnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_bitr3)
   have S16: "( ∃ x ∈ A . ( x = \<cpnf> ∨ x = \<cmnf> ) ) ⟷   
 ( ( ∃ x ∈ A . x = \<cpnf> ∨ ( ∃ x ∈ A . x = \<cmnf> ) ) )" 
     by (rule MMI_r19_43)
   have S17: "( ∃ x ∈ A . x =   
 \<cpnf> ) ⟷ ( ∃ x . ( x ∈ A ∧ x = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_df_rex)
   have S18: "( ∃ x . ( x ∈ A ∧ x = \<cpnf> ) ) ⟷   
 ( ∃ x . ( x = \<cpnf> ∧ x ∈ A ) )" by (rule MMI_exancom)
   have S19: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_pnfxr)
   from S19 have S20: "\<cpnf> isASet" by (rule MMI_elisseti)
   { fix x
     have  "x = \<cpnf> ⟶ ( x ∈ A ⟷ \<cpnf> ∈ A )" by (rule MMI_eleq1)
   } then have S21: "∀ x. x = \<cpnf> ⟶ ( x ∈ A ⟷ \<cpnf> ∈ A )"
     by simp
   from S20 S21 have S22: "( ∃ x . ( x = \<cpnf> ∧ x ∈ A ) ) ⟷ \<cpnf> ∈ A" 
     by (rule MMI_ceqsexv)
   from S17 S18 S22 have S23: "( ∃ x ∈ A . x = \<cpnf> ) ⟷ \<cpnf> ∈ A" 
     by (rule MMI_3bitr)
   have S24: "( ∃ x ∈ A . x =   
 \<cmnf> ) ⟷ ( ∃ x . ( x ∈ A ∧ x = \<cmnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_df_rex)
   have S25: "( ∃ x . ( x ∈ A ∧ x = \<cmnf> ) ) ⟷   
 ( ∃ x . ( x = \<cmnf> ∧ x ∈ A ) )" by (rule MMI_exancom)
   have S26: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_mnfxr)
   from S26 have S27: "\<cmnf> isASet" by (rule MMI_elisseti)
   { fix x 
     have "x = \<cmnf> ⟶ ( x ∈ A ⟷ \<cmnf> ∈ A )" by (rule MMI_eleq1)
   } then have S28: "∀x. x = \<cmnf> ⟶ ( x ∈ A ⟷ \<cmnf> ∈ A )"
     by simp
   from S27 S28 have S29: "( ∃ x . ( x = \<cmnf> ∧ x ∈ A ) ) ⟷ \<cmnf> ∈ A" 
     by (rule MMI_ceqsexv)
   from S24 S25 S29 have S30: "( ∃ x ∈ A . x = \<cmnf> ) ⟷ \<cmnf> ∈ A" 
     by (rule MMI_3bitr)
   from S23 S30 have S31: 
     "( ( ∃ x ∈ A . x = \<cpnf> ∨ ( ∃ x ∈ A . x = \<cmnf> ) ) ) ⟷   
     ( \<cpnf> ∈ A ∨ \<cmnf> ∈ A )" 
     by auto (* by (rule MMI_orbi12i), but I cuould'n get it to work *)
   from S15 S16 S31 have S32: 
     "¬ ( ( ∀ x ∈ A . ¬ ( x ∈ { \<cpnf> , \<cmnf> } ) ) ) ⟷   
     ( \<cpnf> ∈ A ∨ \<cmnf> ∈ A )" by (rule MMI_3bitr)
   from S10 S32 have S33: "( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( ¬ ( A ⊆ ℝ ) ⟶ ( \<cpnf> ∈ A ∨ \<cmnf> ∈ A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_syl6ib)
   from S33 have S34: "( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( A ⊆ ℝ ∨ ( \<cpnf> ∈ A ∨ \<cmnf> ∈ A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_orrd)
   have S35: "( ( A ⊆ ℝ ∨ \<cpnf> ∈ A ∨ \<cmnf> ∈ A ) ⟷   
 ( A ⊆ ℝ ∨ ( \<cpnf> ∈ A ∨ \<cmnf> ∈ A ) ) )" by (rule MMI_3orass)
   from S34 S35 show "( A ⊆ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ( A ⊆ ℝ ∨ \<cpnf> ∈ A ∨ \<cmnf> ∈ A ) )" by (rule MMI_sylibr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_xrltnrt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟷ ( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A = \<cpnf> ∨ A = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_elxr)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_ltnrt)
   have S3: "\<cpnf> ∉ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pnfnre)
   have S4: "\<cpnf> ∉ ℝ ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_df_nel)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S5 have S6: "¬ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S6 have S7: "¬ ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   have S8: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_pnfnemnf)
   have S9: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S10 have S11: "¬ ( ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   from S7 S11 have S12: "¬ ( ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   from S5 have S13: "¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" .
   from S13 have S14: "¬ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   from S5 have S15: "¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" .
   from S15 have S16: "¬ ( ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S14 S16 have S17: "¬ ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   from S12 S17 have S18: "¬ ( ( ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   have S19: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_pnfxr)
   have S20: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_pnfxr)
   have S21: "( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( \<cpnf> \<ls> \<cpnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrt)
   from S19 S20 S21 have S22: "\<cpnf> \<ls> \<cpnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mp2an)
   from S18 S22 have S23: "¬ ( \<cpnf> \<ls> \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_mtbir)
   have S24: "( A = \<cpnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> A ⟷ \<cpnf> \<ls> \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_breq12)
   from S24 have S25: "A = \<cpnf> ⟶ ( A \<ls> A ⟷ \<cpnf> \<ls> \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_anidms)
   from S23 S25 have S26: "A = \<cpnf> ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_mtbiri)
   have S27: "\<cmnf> ∉ ℝ" by (rule MMI_minfnre)
   have S28: "\<cmnf> ∉ ℝ ⟷ ¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_df_nel)
   from S27 S28 have S29: "¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S29 have S30: "¬ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S30 have S31: "¬ ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   have S32: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_pnfnemnf)
   have S33: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf> ⟷ \<cmnf> ≠ \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_necom)
   from S32 S33 have S34: "\<cmnf> ≠ \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   have S35: "\<cmnf> ≠ \<cpnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S34 S35 have S36: "¬ ( \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S36 have S37: "¬ ( ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S31 S37 have S38: "¬ ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   from S29 have S39: "¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" .
   from S39 have S40: "¬ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   from S29 have S41: "¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" .
   from S41 have S42: "¬ ( ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S40 S42 have S43: "¬ ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   from S38 S43 have S44: "¬ ( ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   have S45: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_mnfxr)
   have S46: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_mnfxr)
   have S47: "( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( \<cmnf> \<ls> \<cmnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrt)
   from S45 S46 S47 have S48: "\<cmnf> \<ls> \<cmnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mp2an)
   from S44 S48 have S49: "¬ ( \<cmnf> \<ls> \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_mtbir)
   have S50: "( A = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cmnf> ) ⟶ ( A \<ls> A ⟷ \<cmnf> \<ls> \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_breq12)
   from S50 have S51: "A = \<cmnf> ⟶ ( A \<ls> A ⟷ \<cmnf> \<ls> \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_anidms)
   from S49 S51 have S52: "A = \<cmnf> ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_mtbiri)
   from S2 S26 S52 have S53: "( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A =   
 \<cpnf> ∨ A = \<cmnf> ) ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_3jaoi)
   from S1 S53 show "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_sylbi)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltpnft: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ls> \<cpnf>"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cpnf> = \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_eqid)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_jctr)
   have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> =   
 \<cpnf> ) ⟶   
 ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_orc)
   have S4: "( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶   
 ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_olc)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶   
 ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_3syl)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_rexrt)
   have S7: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_pnfxr)
   have S8: "( A ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> \<cpnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrt)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> \<cpnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan2)
   from S6 S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> \<cpnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S5 S10 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ls> \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_mpbird)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_mnfltt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ \<cmnf> \<ls> A"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cmnf> = \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_eqid)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_jctl)
   have S3: "( \<cmnf> =   
 \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ⟶   
 ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_olc)
   have S4: "( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) ⟶   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_olc)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_3syl)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_rexrt)
   have S7: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_mnfxr)
   have S8: "( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ A ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( \<cmnf> \<ls> A ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrt)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( \<cmnf> \<ls> A ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
   from S6 S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶   
 ( \<cmnf> \<ls> A ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S5 S10 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ \<cmnf> \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_mpbird)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_mnfltpnf: 
   shows "\<cmnf> \<ls> \<cpnf>"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cmnf> = \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_eqid)
   have S2: "\<cpnf> = \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_eqid)
   have S3: "( \<cmnf> =   
 \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> =   
 \<cpnf> ) ⟶   
 ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_olc)
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> =   
 \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_mp2an)
   have S5: "( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ⟶   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_orc)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   have S7: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_mnfxr)
   have S8: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_pnfxr)
   have S9: "( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( \<cmnf> \<ls> \<cpnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrt)
   from S7 S8 S9 have S10: "\<cmnf> \<ls> \<cpnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cmnf> \<lsr> \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cpnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cmnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mp2an)
   from S6 S10 show "\<cmnf> \<ls> \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_mpbir)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_mnfltxrt: 
   shows "( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A = \<cpnf> ) ⟶ \<cmnf> \<ls> A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ \<cmnf> \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_mnfltt)
   have S2: "\<cmnf> \<ls> \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_mnfltpnf)
   have S3: "A = \<cpnf> ⟶ ( \<cmnf> \<ls> A ⟷ \<cmnf> \<ls> \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A = \<cpnf> ⟶ \<cmnf> \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_mpbiri)
   from S1 S4 show "( A ∈ ℝ ∨ A = \<cpnf> ) ⟶ \<cmnf> \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_jaoi)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_pnfnltt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ¬ ( \<cpnf> \<ls> A )"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cpnf> ∉ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pnfnre)
   have S2: "\<cpnf> ∉ ℝ ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_df_nel)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S3 have S4: "¬ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   from S4 have S5: "¬ ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> A ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   have S6: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_pnfnemnf)
   have S7: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S8 have S9: "¬ ( ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   from S5 S9 have S10: "¬ ( ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   from S3 have S11: "¬ ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ )" .
   from S11 have S12: "¬ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   from S8 have S13: "¬ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> )" .
   from S13 have S14: "¬ ( ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "¬ ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   from S10 S15 have S16: "¬ ( ( ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   have S17: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_pnfxr)
   have S18: "( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ A ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( \<cpnf> \<ls> A ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrt)
   from S17 S18 have S19: "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( \<cpnf> \<ls> A ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ∧ \<cpnf> \<lsr> A ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ ∧ A = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( \<cpnf> = \<cmnf> ∧ A ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan)
   from S16 S19 show "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ¬ ( \<cpnf> \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_mtbiri)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_nltmnft: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> \<cmnf> )"
proof -
   have S1: "\<cmnf> ∉ ℝ" by (rule MMI_minfnre)
   have S2: "\<cmnf> ∉ ℝ ⟷ ¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_df_nel)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S3 have S4: "¬ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S4 have S5: "¬ ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnanr)
   have S6: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf>" by (rule MMI_pnfnemnf)
   have S7: "\<cpnf> ≠ \<cmnf> ⟷ \<cmnf> ≠ \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_necom)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "\<cmnf> ≠ \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   have S9: "\<cmnf> ≠ \<cpnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "¬ ( \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> )" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   from S10 have S11: "¬ ( ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S5 S11 have S12: "¬ ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   from S10 have S13: "¬ ( \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> )" .
   from S13 have S14: "¬ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S3 have S15: "¬ ( \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ )" .
   from S15 have S16: "¬ ( ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) )" by (rule MMI_intnan)
   from S14 S16 have S17: "¬ ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   from S12 S17 have S18: "¬ ( ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   have S19: "\<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_mnfxr)
   have S20: "( A ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> \<cmnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_ltxrt)
   from S19 S20 have S21: "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶   
 ( A \<ls> \<cmnf> ⟷   
 ( ( ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ∧ A \<lsr> \<cmnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ) ∨ ( ( A ∈ ℝ ∧ \<cmnf> = \<cpnf> ) ∨ ( A = \<cmnf> ∧ \<cmnf> ∈ ℝ ) ) ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan2)
   from S18 S21 show "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ¬ ( A \<ls> \<cmnf> )" by (rule MMI_mtbiri)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_pnfget: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ A \<lsq> \<cpnf>"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ¬ ( \<cpnf> \<ls> A )" by (rule MMI_pnfnltt)
   have S2: "\<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧*" by (rule MMI_pnfxr)
   have S3: "( A ∈ ℝ⇧* ∧ \<cpnf> ∈ ℝ⇧* ) ⟶   
 ( A \<lsq> \<cpnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_xrlenltt)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ ( A \<lsq> \<cpnf> ⟷ ¬ ( \<cpnf> \<ls> A ) )" by (rule MMI_mpan2)
   from S1 S4 show "A ∈ ℝ⇧* ⟶ A \<lsq> \<cpnf>" by (rule MMI_mpbird)
qed
