 lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_msqge0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬\<lsq>A⋅A"
proof -
   have S1: "A = 𝟬 ⟶ A⋅A = A⋅𝟬" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S3 have S4: "A⋅𝟬 = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul01)
   from S1 S4 have S5: "A = 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟬 = A⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl6req)
   have S6: "𝟬 = A⋅A ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A⋅A ∨ 𝟬 = A⋅A" by (rule MMI_olc)
   from S5 S6 have S7: "A = 𝟬 ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A⋅A ∨ 𝟬 = A⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   have S8: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A1 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S9 S10 have S11: "A⋅A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from S8 S11 have S12: "𝟬\<lsq>A⋅A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>A⋅A ∨ 𝟬 = A⋅A" by (rule MMI_leloe)
   from S7 S12 have S13: "A = 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A⋅A" by (rule MMI_sylibr)
   from A1 have S14: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S14 have S15: "¬(A = 𝟬) ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A⋅A" by (rule MMI_msqgt0)
   have S16: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S17: "A⋅A ∈ ℝ" .
   from S16 S17 have S18: "𝟬\<ls>A⋅A ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A⋅A" by (rule MMI_ltle)
   from S15 S18 have S19: "¬(A = 𝟬) ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S13 S19 show "𝟬\<lsq>A⋅A" by (rule MMI_pm2_61i)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_gt0ne0i: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "𝟬\<ls>A"   
   shows "A ≠ 𝟬"
proof -
   from A2 have S1: "𝟬\<ls>A".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S2 have S3: "𝟬\<ls>A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0)
   from S1 S3 show "A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_gt0ne0t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_neeq1)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<ls>A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ≠ 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S4: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S4 have S5: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S5 have S6: "𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0)
   from S3 S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_dedth)
   from S7 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_letrit: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<lsq>A"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B\<lsq>A ⟷ 
   B\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<lsq>A ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ∨ B\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_orbi12d)
   have S4: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S5: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ∨ B\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ∨ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_orbi12d)
   have S7: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S7 have S8: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S9: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S9 have S10: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S8 S10 have S11: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ∨ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_letri)
   from S3 S6 S11 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<lsq>A" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lelttrit: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<ls>A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A = B ⟶ A\<lsq>B" by (rule MMI_eqlet)
   have S2: "A\<lsq>B ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_orc)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A = B ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A = B ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A = B ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   ¬(A = B) ⟷ A\<ls>B ∨ B\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_lttri2t)
   have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟶ A\<lsq>B" by (rule MMI_ltlet)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ∨ B\<ls>A ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_orim1d)
   from S6 S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   ¬(A = B) ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_sylbid)
   from S5 S9 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<lsq>B ∨ B\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_pm2_61d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltadd1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ A \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A\<ls>B ⟷ A \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S5: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B \<ca> C = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S5 S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S9: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S10: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S9 S10 have S11: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S11 have S12: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi2d)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S13 have S14: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S15: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S15 have S16: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S17: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S17 have S18: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S14 S16 S18 have S19: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_ltadd1)
   from S4 S8 S12 S19 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ A \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltadd2t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ C \<ca> A\<ls>C \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ A \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_ltadd1t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> C = C \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> C = C \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> C = C \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S4 have S9: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S7 S8 S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S10 have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S6 S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<ls>B \<ca> C ⟷ C \<ca> A\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S1 S12 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ C \<ca> A\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_leadd1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S5: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B \<ca> C = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S5 S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S9: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S10: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S9 S10 have S11: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S11 have S12: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> C\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi2d)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S13 have S14: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S15: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S15 have S16: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S17: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S17 have S18: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S14 S16 S18 have S19: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_leadd1)
   from S4 S8 S12 S19 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_leadd2t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ C \<ca> A\<lsq>C \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_leadd1t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> C = C \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> C = C \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> C = C \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S4 have S9: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S7 S8 S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S10 have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S6 S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<lsq>B \<ca> C ⟷ C \<ca> A\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S1 S12 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ C \<ca> A\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_addge01t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>A \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S2: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<ca> 𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_leadd2t)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<ca> 𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_mp3an1)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<ca> 𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_ax0id)
   from S5 S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> 𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B ⟷ A\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S4 S9 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_addge02t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>B \<ca> A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_addge01t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>A \<ca> B ⟷ A\<lsq>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S6 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_subge0t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A \<cs> B ⟷ B\<lsq>A"
proof -
   have S1: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ (\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B\<lsq>A ⟷ 
   B \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>A \<ca> (\<cn>B)" by (rule MMI_leadd1t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegclt)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   from S1 S2 S3 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B\<lsq>A ⟷ 
   B \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>A \<ca> (\<cn>B)" by (rule MMI_syl3anc)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> (\<cn>B) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_negidt)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> (\<cn>B) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   have S9: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> (\<cn>B) = A \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_negsubt)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   B \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>A \<ca> (\<cn>B) ⟷ 𝟬\<lsq>A \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S12: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S10 S11 S12 have S13: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>A \<ca> (\<cn>B) ⟷ 𝟬\<lsq>A \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S6 S13 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A \<cs> B ⟷ B\<lsq>A" by (rule MMI_bitr2d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_subge0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬\<lsq>A \<cs> B ⟷ B\<lsq>A"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A \<cs> B ⟷ B\<lsq>A" by (rule MMI_subge0t)
   from S1 S2 S3 show "𝟬\<lsq>A \<cs> B ⟷ B\<lsq>A" by (rule MMI_mp2an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltsubaddt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B\<ls>C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<ls>C \<ca> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S5: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S5 have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   C \<ca> B = C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S6 S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S10: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S11: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) = ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S11 have S12: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S14: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S14 have S15: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S16: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S16 have S17: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S18: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S18 have S19: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S15 S17 S19 have S20: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_ltsubadd)
   from S4 S9 S13 S20 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltsubadd2t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>B \<ca> C"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_ltsubaddt)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B \<ca> C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S7 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lesubaddt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B\<lsq>C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>C \<ca> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S5: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S5 have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   C \<ca> B = C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S6 S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S10: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S11: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) = ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S11 have S12: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S14: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S14 have S15: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S16: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S16 have S17: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S18: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S18 have S19: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S15 S17 S19 have S20: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_lesubadd)
   from S4 S9 S13 S20 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lesubadd2t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A\<lsq>B \<ca> C"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_lesubaddt)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> C = C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B \<ca> C ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S7 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A\<lsq>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltaddsubt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<cs> B"
proof -
   have S1: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<lsq>A ⟷ C\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_lesubaddt)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<lsq>A ⟷ C\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_3com13)
   have S3: "C \<cs> B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<lsq>A ⟷ ¬(A\<ls>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ C \<cs> B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_resubclt)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<lsq>A ⟷ ¬(A\<ls>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S5 have S6: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<lsq>A ⟷ ¬(A\<ls>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_3impa)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<lsq>A ⟷ ¬(A\<ls>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_3com13)
   have S8: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<ca> B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<lsq>A \<ca> B ⟷ ¬(A \<ca> B\<ls>C)" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axaddrcl)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<lsq>A \<ca> B ⟷ ¬(A \<ca> B\<ls>C)" by (rule MMI_sylan2)
   from S10 have S11: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<lsq>A \<ca> B ⟷ ¬(A \<ca> B\<ls>C)" by (rule MMI_3impb)
   from S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<lsq>A \<ca> B ⟷ ¬(A \<ca> B\<ls>C)" by (rule MMI_3coml)
   from S2 S7 S12 have S13: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   ¬(A \<ca> B\<ls>C) ⟷ ¬(A\<ls>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_3bitr3rd)
   from S13 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_con4bid)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltaddsub2t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<ls>C ⟷ B\<ls>C \<cs> A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<ls>C ⟷ B \<ca> A\<ls>C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B \<ca> A\<ls>C ⟷ B\<ls>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_ltaddsubt)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B \<ca> A\<ls>C ⟷ B\<ls>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S6 S8 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<ls>C ⟷ B\<ls>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_leaddsubt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<cs> B"
proof -
   have S1: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<ls>A ⟷ C\<ls>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_ltsubaddt)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<ls>A ⟷ C\<ls>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_3com13)
   have S3: "C \<cs> B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<ls>A ⟷ ¬(A\<lsq>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_ltnlet)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ C \<cs> B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_resubclt)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<ls>A ⟷ ¬(A\<lsq>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S5 have S6: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<ls>A ⟷ ¬(A\<lsq>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_3impa)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<cs> B\<ls>A ⟷ ¬(A\<lsq>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_3com13)
   have S8: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<ca> B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<ls>A \<ca> B ⟷ ¬(A \<ca> B\<lsq>C)" by (rule MMI_ltnlet)
   have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axaddrcl)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<ls>A \<ca> B ⟷ ¬(A \<ca> B\<lsq>C)" by (rule MMI_sylan2)
   from S10 have S11: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<ls>A \<ca> B ⟷ ¬(A \<ca> B\<lsq>C)" by (rule MMI_3impb)
   from S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<ls>A \<ca> B ⟷ ¬(A \<ca> B\<lsq>C)" by (rule MMI_3coml)
   from S2 S7 S12 have S13: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   ¬(A \<ca> B\<lsq>C) ⟷ ¬(A\<lsq>C \<cs> B)" by (rule MMI_3bitr3rd)
   from S13 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_con4bid)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_sublet: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A \<cs> C\<lsq>B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶

   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> C\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_lesubadd2t)
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> C\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_3com23)
   from S1 S3 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>C ⟷ A \<cs> C\<lsq>B" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lesubt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B \<cs> C ⟷ C\<lsq>B \<cs> A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>B \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_leaddsubt)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>B \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_3com23)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<lsq>B ⟷ C\<lsq>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_leaddsub2t)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<lsq>B ⟷ C\<lsq>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3com23)
   from S2 S4 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B \<cs> C ⟷ C\<lsq>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_bitr3d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltsubadd2: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>B \<ca> C"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℝ".
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_ltsubadd2t)
   from S1 S2 S3 S4 show "A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>B \<ca> C" by (rule MMI_mp3an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltaddsub: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and

    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"

   from S1 S2 S3 S4 show "A \<ca> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_mp3an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmullem: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬\<ls>C ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟶ A⋅C\<ls>B⋅C"
proof -
   from A2 have S1: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "B \<cs> A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_resubcl)
   from A3 have S4: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S3 S4 have S5: "𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>C ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>(B \<cs> A)⋅C" by (rule MMI_mulgt0)
   from S5 have S6: "𝟬\<ls>C ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>(B \<cs> A)⋅C" by (rule MMI_expcom)
   from A1 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S8 have S9: "𝟬 \<ca> A = A" by (rule MMI_addid2)
   from S9 have S10: "𝟬 \<ca> A\<ls>B ⟷ A\<ls>B" by (rule MMI_breq1i)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A1 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S13: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S11 S12 S13 have S14: "𝟬 \<ca> A\<ls>B ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_ltaddsub)
   from S10 S14 have S15: "A\<ls>B ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_bitr3)
   from A2 have S16: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S16 have S17: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S8 have S18: "A ∈ ℂ" .
   from A3 have S19: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S19 have S20: "C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S17 S18 S20 have S21: "(B \<cs> A)⋅C = B⋅C \<cs> A⋅C" by (rule MMI_subdir)
   from S21 have S22: "𝟬\<ls>(B \<cs> A)⋅C ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>B⋅C \<cs> A⋅C" by (rule MMI_breq2i)
   have S23: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A1 have S24: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S25: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S24 S25 have S26: "A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A2 have S27: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S28: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S27 S28 have S29: "B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from S23 S26 S29 have S30: "𝟬 \<ca> A⋅C\<ls>B⋅C ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>B⋅C \<cs> A⋅C" by (rule MMI_ltaddsub)
   from S26 have S31: "A⋅C ∈ ℝ" .
   from S31 have S32: "A⋅C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S32 have S33: "𝟬 \<ca> A⋅C = A⋅C" by (rule MMI_addid2)
   from S33 have S34: "𝟬 \<ca> A⋅C\<ls>B⋅C ⟷ A⋅C\<ls>B⋅C" by (rule MMI_breq1i)
   from S22 S30 S34 have S35: "A⋅C\<ls>B⋅C ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>(B \<cs> A)⋅C" by (rule MMI_3bitr2r)
   from S6 S15 S35 show "𝟬\<ls>C ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟶ A⋅C\<ls>B⋅C" by (rule MMI_3imtr4g)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltsub23t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A \<cs> C\<ls>B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_ltsubaddt)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> C\<ls>B ⟷ A\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_ltsubadd2t)
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> C\<ls>B ⟷ A\<ls>C \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_3com23)
   from S1 S3 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<ls>C ⟷ A \<cs> C\<ls>B" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltsub13t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B \<cs> C ⟷ C\<ls>B \<cs> A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<ls>B ⟷ A\<ls>B \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_ltaddsubt)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> C\<ls>B ⟷ C\<ls>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_ltaddsub2t)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B \<cs> C ⟷ C\<ls>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_bitr3d)
   from S3 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B \<cs> C ⟷ C\<ls>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3com23)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lt2addt: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>C ∧ B\<ls>D ⟶ A \<ca> B\<ls>C \<ca> D"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<ls>C ∧ B\<ls>D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ∧ B\<ls>D" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<ls>C \<ca> D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B\<ls>C \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S2 S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A\<ls>C ∧ B\<ls>D ⟶ A \<ca> B\<ls>C \<ca> D) ⟷ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ∧ B\<ls>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B\<ls>C \<ca> D)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B\<ls>D ⟷ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ∧ B\<ls>D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B\<ls>C \<ca> D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S7 S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ∧ B\<ls>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B\<ls>C \<ca> D) ⟷ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> D)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S11 have S12: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S13: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   C \<ca> D = ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S13 have S14: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>C ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>C \<ca> D) ⟷ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S16: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D ⟷ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S16 have S17: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S18: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D = ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S18 have S19: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S17 S19 have S20: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D) ⟷ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S21: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S21 have S22: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S23: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S23 have S24: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S25: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S25 have S26: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S27: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S27 have S28: " if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S22 S24 S26 S28 have S29: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_lt2add)
   from S5 S10 S15 S20 S29 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>C ∧ B\<ls>D ⟶ A \<ca> B\<ls>C \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_dedth4h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_le2addt: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>C ∧ B\<lsq>D ⟶ A \<ca> B\<lsq>C \<ca> D"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>C ∧ B\<lsq>D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ∧ B\<lsq>D" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B\<lsq>C \<ca> D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B\<lsq>C \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S2 S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A\<lsq>C ∧ B\<lsq>D ⟶ A \<ca> B\<lsq>C \<ca> D) ⟷ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ∧ B\<lsq>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B\<lsq>C \<ca> D)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B\<lsq>D ⟷ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ∧ B\<lsq>D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B\<lsq>C \<ca> D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S7 S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ∧ B\<lsq>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B\<lsq>C \<ca> D) ⟷ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> D)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S11 have S12: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S13: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   C \<ca> D = ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S13 have S14: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>C ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>C \<ca> D) ⟷ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S16: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D ⟷ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S16 have S17: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S18: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D = ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S18 have S19: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S17 S19 have S20: "D =  if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>D ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> D) ⟷ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S21: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S21 have S22: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S23: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S23 have S24: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S25: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S25 have S26: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S27: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S27 have S28: " if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S22 S24 S26 S28 have S29: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(D ∈ ℝ, D, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_le2add)
   from S5 S10 S15 S20 S29 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>C ∧ B\<lsq>D ⟶ A \<ca> B\<lsq>C \<ca> D" by (rule MMI_dedth4h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_addgt0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S2 S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S13 have S14: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_addgt0)
   from S5 S10 S15 have S16: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S16 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_addgegt0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S2 S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S13 have S14: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_addgegt0)
   from S5 S10 S15 have S16: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S16 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<ls>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_addgtge0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_addgegt0t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟷ 
   B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ancom)
   have S3: "𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_ancom)
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_syl2anb)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S5 S6 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S8 have S9: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S4 S9 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<ls>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breqtrrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_addge0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S2 S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S13 have S14: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ca> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_addge0)
   from S5 S10 S15 have S16: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S16 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltaddpost: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S2: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B \<ca> 𝟬\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_ltadd2t)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B \<ca> 𝟬\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_mp3an1)
   have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S5: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> 𝟬 = B" by (rule MMI_ax0id)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> 𝟬 = B" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> 𝟬 = B" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B \<ca> 𝟬\<ls>B \<ca> A ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S3 S8 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltaddpos2t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>A \<ca> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_ltaddpost)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_axaddcom)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> B = B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B\<ls>A \<ca> B ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S6 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_subge02t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<cs> B\<lsq>A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_addge01t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>A ⟷ A\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_lesubaddt)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S3 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" .
   from S2 S3 S4 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> B\<lsq>A ⟷ A\<lsq>A \<ca> B" by (rule MMI_syl3anc)
   from S1 S6 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<cs> B\<lsq>A" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltsubpost: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B \<cs> A\<ls>B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_ltaddpost)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B \<cs> A\<ls>B ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_ltsubaddt)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S3 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" .
   from S2 S3 S4 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B \<cs> A\<ls>B ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_syl3anc)
   from S1 S6 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B \<cs> A\<ls>B" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_posdift: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A"
proof -
   have S1: "B \<cs> A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A ⟷ A\<ls>A \<ca> (B \<cs> A)" by (rule MMI_ltaddpost)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<cs> A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_resubclt)
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<cs> A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S1 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A ⟷ A\<ls>A \<ca> (B \<cs> A)" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> (B \<cs> A) = B" by (rule MMI_pncan3t)
   have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S6 S7 S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> (B \<cs> A) = B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>A \<ca> (B \<cs> A) ⟷ A\<ls>B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S5 S10 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_bitr2d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltnegt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A)"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A) = (\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_negeq)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>B ⟷ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S5: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B) = (\<cn>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_negeq)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   (\<cn>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))\<ls>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S5 S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>B ⟷ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   (\<cn>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))\<ls>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S9: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S9 have S10: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<ls>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   (\<cn>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))\<ls>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_ltneg)
   from S4 S8 S13 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltnegcon1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A)\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>A"
proof -
   have S1: "(\<cn>A) ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A)\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>(\<cn>A))" by (rule MMI_ltnegt)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>A) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegclt)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A)\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>(\<cn>A))" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ (\<cn>(\<cn>A)) = A" by (rule MMI_negnegt)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>(\<cn>A)) = A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>(\<cn>A)) ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>(\<cn>A)) ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S3 S8 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A)\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lenegt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A)"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A) = (\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_negeq)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A\<lsq>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S5: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B) = (\<cn>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_negeq)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   (\<cn>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))\<lsq>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S5 S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   (\<cn>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))\<lsq>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S9: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S9 have S10: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   (\<cn>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))\<lsq>(\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_leneg)
   from S4 S8 S13 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lenegcon2t:

   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>(\<cn>B)) = B" by (rule MMI_adantl)

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lesub1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<cs> C\<lsq>B \<cs> C"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ (\<cn>C) ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   A \<ca> (\<cn>C)\<lsq>B \<ca> (\<cn>C)" by (rule MMI_leadd1t)
   have S2: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>C) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegclt)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   A \<ca> (\<cn>C)\<lsq>B \<ca> (\<cn>C)" by (rule MMI_syl3an3)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> (\<cn>C) = A \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_negsubt)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> (\<cn>C) = A \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> (\<cn>C) = B \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_negsubt)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B \<ca> (\<cn>C) = B \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S5 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> (\<cn>C)\<lsq>B \<ca> (\<cn>C) ⟷ A \<cs> C\<lsq>B \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S11: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S8 S9 S10 S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> (\<cn>C)\<lsq>B \<ca> (\<cn>C) ⟷ A \<cs> C\<lsq>B \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_syl3an)
   from S3 S12 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ A \<cs> C\<lsq>B \<cs> C" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lesub2t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ C \<cs> B\<lsq>C \<cs> A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_lenegt)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S3: "(\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ ∧ (\<cn>A) ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>C \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_leadd2t)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>A) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegclt)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "(\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>C \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_syl3an2)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegclt)
   from S5 S6 have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>C \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_syl3an1)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<lsq>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>C \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   have S9: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ C \<ca> (\<cn>B) = C \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_negsubt)
   from S9 have S10: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ C \<ca> (\<cn>B) = C \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S11: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ⟶ C \<ca> (\<cn>A) = C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_negsubt)
   from S11 have S12: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ C \<ca> (\<cn>A) = C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>C \<ca> (\<cn>A) ⟷ C \<cs> B\<lsq>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S13 have S14: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>C \<ca> (\<cn>A) ⟷ C \<cs> B\<lsq>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3coml)
   have S15: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S16: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S17: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S14 S15 S16 S17 have S18: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<lsq>C \<ca> (\<cn>A) ⟷ C \<cs> B\<lsq>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_syl3an)
   from S2 S8 S18 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<lsq>B ⟷ C \<cs> B\<lsq>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltsub2t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ C \<cs> B\<ls>C \<cs> A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_ltnegt)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S3: "(\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ ∧ (\<cn>A) ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<ls>C \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_ltadd2t)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>A) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegclt)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "(\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<ls>C \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_syl3an2)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ (\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegclt)
   from S5 S6 have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<ls>C \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_syl3an1)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>B)\<ls>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<ls>C \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   have S9: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ C \<ca> (\<cn>B) = C \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_negsubt)
   from S9 have S10: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ C \<ca> (\<cn>B) = C \<cs> B" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S11: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ⟶ C \<ca> (\<cn>A) = C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_negsubt)
   from S11 have S12: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ C \<ca> (\<cn>A) = C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<ls>C \<ca> (\<cn>A) ⟷ C \<cs> B\<ls>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S13 have S14: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<ls>C \<ca> (\<cn>A) ⟷ C \<cs> B\<ls>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3coml)
   have S15: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S16: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S17: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S14 S15 S16 S17 have S18: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C \<ca> (\<cn>B)\<ls>C \<ca> (\<cn>A) ⟷ C \<cs> B\<ls>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_syl3an)
   from S2 S8 S18 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ C \<cs> B\<ls>C \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_3bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltaddpos: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_ltaddpost)
   from S1 S2 S3 show "𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ B\<ls>B \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_mp2an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_posdif: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "A\<ls>B ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>B ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_posdift)
   from S1 S2 S3 show "A\<ls>B ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>B \<cs> A" by (rule MMI_mp2an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lt0neg1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>(\<cn>A)"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>𝟬)\<ls>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_ltnegt)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>𝟬)\<ls>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_mpan2)
   have S4: "(\<cn>𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_neg0)
   from S4 have S5: "(\<cn>𝟬)\<ls>(\<cn>A) ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_breq1i)
   from S3 S5 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬\<ls>(\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_syl6bb)
qed

   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ (\<cn>A)\<ls>(\<cn>𝟬)" by (rule MMI_ltnegt)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ (\<cn>A)\<ls>(\<cn>𝟬)" by (rule MMI_mpan)
   have S4: "(\<cn>𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_neg0)
   from S4 have S5: "(\<cn>A)\<ls>(\<cn>𝟬) ⟷ (\<cn>A)\<ls>𝟬" by (rule MMI_breq2i)
   from S3 S5 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ (\<cn>A)\<ls>𝟬" by (rule MMI_syl6bb)
qed

   𝟬\<lsq>A ⟷ (\<cn>A)\<lsq>𝟬"

   from S3 S5 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ⟷ (\<cn>A)\<lsq>𝟬" by (rule MMI_syl6bb)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lesub0t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ B\<lsq>B \<cs> A ⟷ A = 𝟬"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B \<cs> A = B \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B\<lsq>B \<cs> A ⟷ 
   B\<lsq>B \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ B\<lsq>B \<cs> A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ B\<lsq>B \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi12d)
   have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A = 𝟬 ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqeq1)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ B\<lsq>B \<cs> A ⟷ A = 𝟬) ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ B\<lsq>B \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_id)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B\<lsq>B \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ B\<lsq>B \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   from S10 have S11: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ B\<lsq>B \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬) ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_bibi1d)
   have S12: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S12 have S13: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S14: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S14 have S15: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S13 S15 have S16: "𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<cs> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_lesub0)
   from S6 S11 S16 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ B\<lsq>B \<cs> A ⟷ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_mulge0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S2 S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A⋅B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S13 have S14: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_mulge0)
   from S5 S10 S15 have S16: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A⋅B" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S16 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>A ∧ 𝟬\<lsq>B ⟶ 𝟬\<lsq>A⋅B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmsqt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   ¬(A = 𝟬) ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A⋅A"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A = 𝟬 ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqeq1)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ¬(A = 𝟬) ⟷ 
   ¬( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_negbid)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_id)
   from S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)" .
   from S3 S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅A = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq12d)
   from S5 have S6: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A⋅A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S2 S6 have S7: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (¬(A = 𝟬) ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A⋅A) ⟷ 
   (¬( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S8: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S8 have S9: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S9 have S10: "¬( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_msqgt0)
   from S7 S10 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   ¬(A = 𝟬) ⟶ 𝟬\<ls>A⋅A" by (rule MMI_dedth)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lt01: 
   shows "𝟬\<ls>𝟭"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟭 ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ax1ne0)
   have S2: "𝟭 ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ ¬(𝟭 = 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "¬(𝟭 = 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   have S4: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S4 have S5: "¬(𝟭 = 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>𝟭⋅𝟭" by (rule MMI_msqgt0)
   from S3 S5 have S6: "𝟬\<ls>𝟭⋅𝟭" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   have S7: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from S7 have S8: "𝟭⋅𝟭 = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_mulid1)
   from S6 S8 show "𝟬\<ls>𝟭" by (rule MMI_breqtr)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_eqneg: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ A = 𝟬"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S2: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_readdcl)
   have S4: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S5: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S6: "𝟬\<ls>𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   have S7: "𝟬\<ls>𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   from S4 S5 S6 S7 have S8: "𝟬\<ls>𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_addgt0i)
   from S3 S8 have S9: "𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0i)
   have S10: "𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ 
   ¬(𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 = 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S9 S10 have S11: "¬(𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 = 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   have S12: "A = (\<cn>A) ⟶ A \<ca> A = A \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from A1 have S13: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from S13 have S14: "(𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭)⋅A = A \<ca> A" by (rule MMI_1p1times)
   from A1 have S15: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from S15 have S16: "A \<ca> (\<cn>A) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_negid)
   from S16 have S17: "𝟬 = A \<ca> (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_eqcomi)
   from S12 S14 S17 have S18: "A = (\<cn>A) ⟶ 
   (𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭)⋅A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_3eqtr4g)
   from S3 have S19: "𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ" .
   from S19 have S20: "𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A1 have S21: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from S20 S21 have S22: "(𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭)⋅A = 𝟬 ⟷ 
   𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 = 𝟬 ∨ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul0or)
   from S18 S22 have S23: "A = (\<cn>A) ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 = 𝟬 ∨ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_sylib)
   from S23 have S24: "A = (\<cn>A) ⟶ 
   ¬(𝟭 \<ca> 𝟭 = 𝟬) ⟶ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ord)
   from S11 S24 have S25: "A = (\<cn>A) ⟶ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mpi)
   have S26: "(\<cn>𝟬) = 𝟬 \<cs> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_df_neg)
   have S27: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S27 have S28: "𝟬 \<cs> 𝟬 = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_subid)
   from S26 S28 have S29: "𝟬 = (\<cn>𝟬)" by (rule MMI_eqtr2)
   have S30: "A = 𝟬 ⟶ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_id)
   have S31: "A = 𝟬 ⟶ (\<cn>A) = (\<cn>𝟬)" by (rule MMI_negeq)
   from S30 S31 have S32: "A = 𝟬 ⟶ 
   A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ 𝟬 = (\<cn>𝟬)" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   from S29 S32 have S33: "A = 𝟬 ⟶ A = (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_mpbiri)
   from S25 S33 show "A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_impbi)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_eqnegt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ A = 𝟬"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A =  if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_id)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A) = (\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_negeq)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) = (\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_eqeq12d)
   have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A = 𝟬 ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqeq1)
   from S3 S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ A = 𝟬) ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) = (\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S6: "𝟬 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_0cn)
   from S6 have S7: " if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S7 have S8: " if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) = (\<cn>( if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
    if(A ∈ ℂ, A, 𝟬) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqneg)
   from S5 S8 show "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_dedth)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_negeq0t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A = 𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>A) = 𝟬"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ (\<cn>(\<cn>A)) = A" by (rule MMI_negnegt)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A) = (\<cn>(\<cn>A)) ⟷ (\<cn>A) = A" by (rule MMI_eqeq2d)
   have S3: "(\<cn>A) = A ⟷ A = (\<cn>A)" by (rule MMI_eqcom)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ (\<cn>A) = (\<cn>(\<cn>A))" by (rule MMI_syl6rbb)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A = (\<cn>A) ⟷ A = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqnegt)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ (\<cn>A) ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_negclt)
   have S7: "(\<cn>A) ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A) = (\<cn>(\<cn>A)) ⟷ (\<cn>A) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqnegt)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   (\<cn>A) = (\<cn>(\<cn>A)) ⟷ (\<cn>A) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S4 S5 S8 show "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A = 𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>A) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_3bitr3d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_negne0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ"   
   shows "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>A) ≠ 𝟬"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℂ".
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A = 𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>A) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_negeq0t)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A = 𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>A) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from S3 show "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>A) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqneqi)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_negn0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℂ" and
    A2: "A ≠ 𝟬"   
   shows "(\<cn>A) ≠ 𝟬"
proof -
   from A2 have S1: "A ≠ 𝟬".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℂ".
   from S2 have S3: "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ (\<cn>A) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_negne0)
   from S1 S3 show "(\<cn>A) ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_elimgt0: 
   shows "𝟬\<ls>( if(𝟬\<ls>A, A, 𝟭))"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(𝟬\<ls>A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(𝟬\<ls>A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S2: "𝟭 =  if(𝟬\<ls>A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>𝟭 ⟷ 
   𝟬\<ls>( if(𝟬\<ls>A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S3: "𝟬\<ls>𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   from S1 S2 S3 show "𝟬\<ls>( if(𝟬\<ls>A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_elimhyp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_elimge0: 
   shows "𝟬\<lsq>( if(𝟬\<lsq>A, A, 𝟬))"

   𝟬\<lsq>( if(𝟬\<lsq>A, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)

   𝟬\<lsq>𝟬 ⟷ 
   𝟬\<lsq>( if(𝟬\<lsq>A, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S3: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S3 have S4: "𝟬\<lsq>𝟬" by (rule MMI_leid)
   from S1 S2 S4 show "𝟬\<lsq>( if(𝟬\<lsq>A, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_elimhyp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltp1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<ls>A \<ca> 𝟭"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<ca> 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_ax0id)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   have S4: "𝟬\<ls>𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   have S5: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S6: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S7: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>𝟭 ⟷ 
   A \<ca> 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_ltadd2t)
   from S5 S6 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬\<ls>𝟭 ⟷ 
   A \<ca> 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_mp3an12)
   from S4 S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> 𝟬\<ls>A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_mpbii)
   from S3 S9 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<ls>A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_eqbrtrrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lep1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<lsq>A \<ca> 𝟭"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<ls>A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_ltp1t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_peano2re)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>A \<ca> 𝟭 ⟶ A\<lsq>A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_ltlet)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<ls>A \<ca> 𝟭 ⟶ A\<lsq>A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_mpdan)
   from S1 S4 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A\<lsq>A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_mpd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltp1: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ"
