lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recgt0i: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "𝟬 \<ls> A"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟭 ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_1cn)
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   have S4: "𝟭 ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ax1ne0)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S6: "𝟬 \<ls> A".
   from S5 S6 have S7: "A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0i)
   from S1 S3 S4 S7 have S8: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_divne0)
   have S9: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ≠ 𝟬 ⟷ 
   𝟬 ≠ 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_necom)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "𝟬 ≠ 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   have S11: "𝟬 ≠ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   ¬(𝟬 = 𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_df_ne)
   from S10 S11 have S12: "¬(𝟬 = 𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_mpbi)
   have S13: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   have S14: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S15: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S14 S15 have S16: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭 ⟶ ¬(𝟭 \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_ltnsym)
   from S13 S16 have S17: "¬(𝟭 \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from A2 have S18: "𝟬 \<ls> A".
   from A1 have S19: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S7 have S20: "A ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S19 S20 have S21: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rereccl)
   from S21 have S22: "(\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A)) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegcl)
   from A1 have S23: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S22 S23 have S24: "𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A))⋅A" by (rule MMI_mulgt0)
   from S18 S24 have S25: "𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A)) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A))⋅A" by (rule MMI_mpan2)
   from S21 have S26: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" .
   from S26 have S27: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S3 have S28: "A ∈ ℂ" .
   from S27 S28 have S29: "(\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A))⋅A = (\<cn>((𝟭\<cdiv>A)⋅A))" by (rule MMI_mulneg1)
   from S27 have S30: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℂ" .
   from S3 have S31: "A ∈ ℂ" .
   from S30 S31 have S32: "(𝟭\<cdiv>A)⋅A = A⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_mulcom)
   from S3 have S33: "A ∈ ℂ" .
   from S7 have S34: "A ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S33 S34 have S35: "A⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_recid)
   from S32 S35 have S36: "(𝟭\<cdiv>A)⋅A = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_eqtr)
   from S36 have S37: "(\<cn>((𝟭\<cdiv>A)⋅A)) = (\<cn>𝟭)" by (rule MMI_negeqi)
   from S29 S37 have S38: "(\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A))⋅A = (\<cn>𝟭)" by (rule MMI_eqtr)
   from S25 S38 have S39: "𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A)) ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>𝟭)" by (rule MMI_syl6breq)
   from S21 have S40: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" .
   have S41: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A))" by (rule MMI_lt0neg1t)
   from S40 S41 have S42: "𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(𝟭\<cdiv>A))" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   have S43: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S44: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>𝟭)" by (rule MMI_lt0neg1t)
   from S43 S44 have S45: "𝟭 \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>𝟭)" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from S39 S42 S45 have S46: "𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_3imtr4)
   from S17 S46 have S47: "¬(𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_mto)
   from S12 S47 have S48: "¬(𝟬 = 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∨ 𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_pm3_2ni)
   have S49: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S21 have S50: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" .
   have S51: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   ¬(𝟬 = 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∨ 𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_axlttri)
   from S49 S50 S51 have S52: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   ¬(𝟬 = 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∨ 𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_mp2an)
   from S48 S52 show "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_mpbir)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltm1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<cs> 𝟭 \<ls> A"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   have S2: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S3: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S4: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭 ⟷ 
   A \<cs> 𝟭 \<ls> A \<cs> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ltsub2t)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭 ⟷ 
   A \<cs> 𝟭 \<ls> A \<cs> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mp3an12)
   from S1 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<cs> 𝟭 \<ls> A \<cs> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mpbii)
   have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S8: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ A \<cs> 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_subid1t)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<cs> 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S6 S9 show "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<cs> 𝟭 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_breqtrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_letrp1t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B \<ca> 𝟭"
proof -
   have S1: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_ltp1t)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭 ⟶ A \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_lelttrt)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭 ⟶ A \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_3expb)
   have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_peano2re)
   from S5 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ∧ B \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ancli)
   from S4 S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ∧ B \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭 ⟶ A \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_sylan2)
   from S2 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_mpan2d)
   from S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_3impia)
   have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭 ⟶ A \<lsq> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_ltlet)
   from S5 have S11: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ" .
   from S10 S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭 ⟶ A \<lsq> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_sylan2)
   from S12 have S13: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B \<ca> 𝟭 ⟶ A \<lsq> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S9 S13 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_mpd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_p1let: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<lsq> A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_lep1t)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<lsq> A \<ca> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> A \<ca> 𝟭 ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_letrt)
   from S3 have S4: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> A \<ca> 𝟭 ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_peano2re)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ancli)
   from S4 S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> A \<ca> 𝟭 ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S2 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ca> 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_mpand)
   from S8 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A \<ca> 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_3impia)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_prodgt0lem: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "𝟬 \<ls> A"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S2: "𝟬 \<ls> A".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_recgt0i)
   have S4: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S5 S6 have S7: "A⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A1 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S10: "𝟬 \<ls> A".
   from S9 S10 have S11: "A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0i)
   from S8 S11 have S12: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rereccl)
   from S4 S7 S12 have S13: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 
   𝟬⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A) \<ls> A⋅B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_ltmullem)
   from S3 S13 have S14: "𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 
   𝟬⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A) \<ls> A⋅B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from S12 have S15: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" .
   from S15 have S16: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S16 have S17: "𝟬⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A) = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul02)
   from A1 have S18: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S18 have S19: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A2 have S20: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S20 have S21: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S16 have S22: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℂ" .
   from S19 S21 S22 have S23: "A⋅B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A) = A⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)⋅B" by (rule MMI_mul23)
   from S19 have S24: "A ∈ ℂ" .
   from S11 have S25: "A ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S24 S25 have S26: "A⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_recid)
   from S26 have S27: "A⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)⋅B = 𝟭⋅B" by (rule MMI_opreq1i)
   from S21 have S28: "B ∈ ℂ" .
   from S28 have S29: "𝟭⋅B = B" by (rule MMI_mulid2)
   from S23 S27 S29 have S30: "A⋅B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A) = B" by (rule MMI_3eqtr)
   from S14 S17 S30 show "𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_3brtr3g)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_prodgt0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∨ 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_leloe)
   have S4: "A =  if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   A⋅B = ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))⋅B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S5 have S6: "A =  if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B)" by (rule MMI_imbi1d)
   from A1 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ".
   have S8: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S7 S8 have S9: " if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   from A2 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ".
   have S11: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_elimgt0)
   from S9 S10 S11 have S12: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_prodgt0lem)
   from S6 S12 have S13: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_dedth)
   have S14: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S14 have S15: "¬(𝟬 \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_ltnr)
   have S16: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 𝟬⋅B = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from A2 have S17: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S17 have S18: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S18 have S19: "𝟬⋅B = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul02)
   from S16 S19 have S20: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 𝟬 = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl5eqr)
   from S20 have S21: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S15 S21 have S22: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   ¬(𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B)" by (rule MMI_mtbii)
   from S22 have S23: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_pm2_21d)
   from S13 S23 have S24: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∨ 𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_jaoi)
   from S3 S24 have S25: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_sylbi)
   from S25 show "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_prodge0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S2 have S3: "(\<cn>B) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_renegcl)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>B) ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅(\<cn>B)" by (rule MMI_mulgt0)
   from S4 have S5: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>B) ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅(\<cn>B)" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ".
   have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>B)" by (rule MMI_lt0neg1t)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "B \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>B)" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from A1 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S9 S10 have S11: "A⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   have S12: "A⋅B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(A⋅B))" by (rule MMI_lt0neg1t)
   from S11 S12 have S13: "A⋅B \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(A⋅B))" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from A1 have S14: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S14 have S15: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A2 have S16: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S16 have S17: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S15 S17 have S18: "A⋅(\<cn>B) = (\<cn>(A⋅B))" by (rule MMI_mulneg2)
   from S18 have S19: "𝟬 \<ls> A⋅(\<cn>B) ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> (\<cn>(A⋅B))" by (rule MMI_breq2i)
   from S13 S19 have S20: "A⋅B \<ls> 𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅(\<cn>B)" by (rule MMI_bitr4)
   from S5 S8 S20 have S21: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   B \<ls> 𝟬 ⟶ A⋅B \<ls> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_3imtr4g)
   from S21 have S22: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   ¬(A⋅B \<ls> 𝟬) ⟶ ¬(B \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_con3d)
   have S23: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S24: "A⋅B ∈ ℝ" .
   from S23 S24 have S25: "𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟷ 
   ¬(A⋅B \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_lenlt)
   have S26: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A2 have S27: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S26 S27 have S28: "𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬(B \<ls> 𝟬)" by (rule MMI_lenlt)
   from S22 S25 S28 have S29: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_3imtr4g)
   from S29 show "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmul1i: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ" and
    A4: "𝟬 \<ls> C"   
   shows "A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C"
proof -
   from A4 have S1: "𝟬 \<ls> C".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S3: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S4: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_ltmullem)
   from S1 S5 have S6: "A \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from A3 have S7: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from A4 have S8: "𝟬 \<ls> C".
   from S7 S8 have S9: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_recgt0i)
   from A1 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S11: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S10 S11 have S12: "A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A2 have S13: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S14: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S13 S14 have S15: "B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A3 have S16: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S17: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from A4 have S18: "𝟬 \<ls> C".
   from S17 S18 have S19: "C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0i)
   from S16 S19 have S20: "𝟭\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rereccl)
   from S12 S15 S20 have S21: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>C ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟶ 
   A⋅C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) \<ls> B⋅C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_ltmullem)
   from S9 S21 have S22: "A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟶ 
   A⋅C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) \<ls> B⋅C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from A1 have S23: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S23 have S24: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A3 have S25: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S25 have S26: "C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S26 have S27: "C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S19 have S28: "C ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S27 S28 have S29: "𝟭\<cdiv>C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_reccl)
   from S24 S26 S29 have S30: "A⋅C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) = A⋅(C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C))" by (rule MMI_mulass)
   from S26 have S31: "C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S19 have S32: "C ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S31 S32 have S33: "C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_recid)
   from S33 have S34: "A⋅(C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C)) = A⋅𝟭" by (rule MMI_opreq2i)
   from S24 have S35: "A ∈ ℂ" .
   from S35 have S36: "A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_mulid1)
   from S30 S34 S36 have S37: "A⋅C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) = A" by (rule MMI_3eqtr)
   from A2 have S38: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S38 have S39: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S26 have S40: "C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S29 have S41: "𝟭\<cdiv>C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S39 S40 S41 have S42: "B⋅C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) = B⋅(C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C))" by (rule MMI_mulass)
   from S33 have S43: "C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) = 𝟭" .
   from S43 have S44: "B⋅(C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C)) = B⋅𝟭" by (rule MMI_opreq2i)
   from S39 have S45: "B ∈ ℂ" .
   from S45 have S46: "B⋅𝟭 = B" by (rule MMI_mulid1)
   from S42 S44 S46 have S47: "B⋅C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) = B" by (rule MMI_3eqtr)
   from S22 S37 S47 have S48: "A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟶ A \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_3brtr3g)
   from S6 S48 show "A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_impbi)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmul1: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C"
proof -
   have S1: "C =  if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   A⋅C = A⋅( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S2: "C =  if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   B⋅C = B⋅( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "C =  if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ 
   A⋅( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭)) \<ls> B⋅( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S3 have S4: "C =  if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   (A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C) ⟷ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   A⋅( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭)) \<ls> B⋅( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_bibi2d)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S7: "C ∈ ℝ".
   have S8: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S7 S8 have S9: " if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   have S10: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_elimgt0)
   from S5 S6 S9 S10 have S11: "A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   A⋅( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭)) \<ls> B⋅( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_ltmul1i)
   from S4 S11 show "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_dedth)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltdiv1i: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ" and
    A4: "𝟬 \<ls> C"   
   shows "A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S4: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from A4 have S5: "𝟬 \<ls> C".
   from S4 S5 have S6: "C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0i)
   from S3 S6 have S7: "𝟭\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rereccl)
   from A3 have S8: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from A4 have S9: "𝟬 \<ls> C".
   from S8 S9 have S10: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_recgt0i)
   from S1 S2 S7 S10 have S11: "A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   A⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) \<ls> B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_ltmul1i)
   from A1 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S12 have S13: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A3 have S14: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S14 have S15: "C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S6 have S16: "C ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S13 S15 S16 have S17: "A\<cdiv>C = A⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_divrec)
   from A2 have S18: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S18 have S19: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S15 have S20: "C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S6 have S21: "C ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S19 S20 S21 have S22: "B\<cdiv>C = B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_divrec)
   from S17 S22 have S23: "A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C ⟷ 
   A⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C) \<ls> B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_breq12i)
   from S11 S23 show "A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_bitr4)
qed

(*********** 411 - 420 ********************************)

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltdiv1: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C"
proof -
   have S1: "C =  if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C = A\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S2: "C =  if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   B\<cdiv>C = B\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "C =  if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭)) \<ls> B\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S3 have S4: "C =  if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   (A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C) ⟷ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭)) \<ls> B\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_bibi2d)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S7: "C ∈ ℝ".
   have S8: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S7 S8 have S9: " if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   have S10: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_elimgt0)
   from S5 S6 S9 S10 have S11: "A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭)) \<ls> B\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> C, C, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_ltdiv1i)
   from S4 S11 show "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_dedth)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmuldiv: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B\<cdiv>C"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S2: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A2 have S4: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S5: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S3 S4 S5 have S6: "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B ⟷ 
   A⋅C\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_ltdiv1)
   from A3 have S7: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S7 have S8: "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0)
   from A3 have S9: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S9 have S10: "C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A1 have S11: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A⋅C\<cdiv>C = A" by (rule MMI_divcan4z)
   from S8 S13 have S14: "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ A⋅C\<cdiv>C = A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S14 have S15: "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A⋅C\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C ⟷ A \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S6 S15 show "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_prodgt0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_anbi12d)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B)" by (rule MMI_imbi1d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S13 have S14: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_prodgt0)
   from S5 S10 S15 have S16: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S16 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_prodgt02t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A"
proof -
   have S1: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B⋅A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_prodgt0t)
   from S1 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B⋅A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B⋅A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅B = B⋅A" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S4 S5 S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅B = B⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> B⋅A" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B⋅A" by (rule MMI_biimpd)
   from S3 S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_sylan2d)
   from S10 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_prodge0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_anbi12d)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B)" by (rule MMI_imbi1d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S13: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S13 have S14: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S12 S14 have S15: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_prodge0)
   from S5 S10 S15 have S16: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S16 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_prodge02t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A"
proof -
   have S1: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅A ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_prodge0t)
   from S1 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅A ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅A ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅B = B⋅A" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S4 S5 S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅B = B⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅A" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅A" by (rule MMI_biimpd)
   from S3 S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_sylan2d)
   from S10 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmul1t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅C = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> B⋅C)" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B⋅C = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅C" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅C" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S6 S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> B⋅C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅C" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> B⋅C) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅C)" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S11: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S12: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S13: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅C = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S12 S13 have S14: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S14 have S15: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi2d)
   from S11 S15 have S16: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅C) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S17: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S17 have S18: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S19: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S19 have S20: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S21: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S21 have S22: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S18 S20 S22 have S23: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_ltmul1)
   from S5 S10 S16 S23 have S24: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
   from S24 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmul2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_ltmul1t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S5 S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   have S11: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S10 S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl3an3)
   from S12 have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S1 S13 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemul1t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_ltmul1t)
   have S2: "(A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   A⋅C = B⋅C ⟷ A = B" by (rule MMI_mulcan2t)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S5: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S3 S4 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3anim123i)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S8: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S8 have S9: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantll)
   from S9 have S10: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_3adantl2)
   from S2 S7 S10 have S11: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A⋅C = B⋅C ⟷ A = B" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S11 have S12: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A = B ⟷ A⋅C = B⋅C" by (rule MMI_bicomd)
   from S1 S12 have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ⟷ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ∨ A⋅C = B⋅C" by (rule MMI_orbi12d)
   have S14: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A \<ls> B ∨ A = B" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   from S14 have S15: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A \<ls> B ∨ A = B" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S15 have S16: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A \<ls> B ∨ A = B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S17: "A⋅C ∈ ℝ ∧ B⋅C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C ⟷ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ∨ A⋅C = B⋅C" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   have S18: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S18 have S19: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S20: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S20 have S21: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S17 S19 S21 have S22: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C ⟷ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ∨ A⋅C = B⋅C" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S22 have S23: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C ⟷ 
   A⋅C \<ls> B⋅C ∨ A⋅C = B⋅C" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S13 S16 S23 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_3bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemul2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_lemul1t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S4 have S9: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S7 S8 S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S10 have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S6 S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C ⟷ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S12 have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C ⟷ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S1 S13 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmul2: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℝ".
   have S4: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltmul2t)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S1 S2 S3 S5 show "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C⋅A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_mp3an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemul1: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℝ".
   have S4: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_lemul1t)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S1 S2 S3 S5 show "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_mp3an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemul2: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℝ".
   have S4: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_lemul2t)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S1 S2 S3 S5 show "𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_mp3an)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemul1it: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S2: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> C ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ∨ 𝟬 = C" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> C ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ∨ 𝟬 = C" by (rule MMI_mpan)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> C ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ∨ 𝟬 = C" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant3)
   have S5: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_lemul1t)
   from S5 have S6: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_biimpd)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_ex)
   have S8: "𝟬 = C ⟶ A⋅𝟬 = A⋅C" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S9: "𝟬 = C ⟶ B⋅𝟬 = B⋅C" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S8 S9 have S10: "𝟬 = C ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅𝟬 ⟷ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   have S11: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S11 have S12: "𝟬 \<lsq> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_leid)
   have S13: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅𝟬 = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul01t)
   have S14: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅𝟬 = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul01t)
   from S13 S14 have S15: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsq> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_breqan12d)
   have S16: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S17: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S15 S16 S17 have S18: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅𝟬 ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsq> 𝟬" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S12 S18 have S19: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟬 \<lsq> B⋅𝟬" by (rule MMI_mpbiri)
   from S10 S19 have S20: "𝟬 = C ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_syl5bi)
   from S20 have S21: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 = C ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_com12)
   from S21 have S22: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 = C ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S22 have S23: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 = C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_a1dd)
   from S7 S23 have S24: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ∨ 𝟬 = C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_jaod)
   from S4 S24 have S25: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_sylbid)
   from S25 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_imp32)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemul2it: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_lemul1it)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C = C⋅A" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S9: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S4 have S10: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S8 S9 S10 have S11: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S11 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S12 have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S1 S7 S13 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ C⋅A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_3brtr3d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmul12it: 
   shows "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅D"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_lemul1it)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S2 have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S4 have S5: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S6: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   from S3 S5 S7 have S8: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   from S8 have S9: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S10: "𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> C" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S10 have S11: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> C" by (rule MMI_ad2antll)
   have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_ltlet)
   from S12 have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S13 have S14: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_adantrl)
   from S14 have S15: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2r)
   from S11 S15 have S16: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S1 S9 S16 have S17: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S18: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C \<ls> D ⟷ B⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_ltmul2t)
   from S7 have S19: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" .
   have S20: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S20 have S21: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   from S5 have S22: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" .
   from S19 S21 S22 have S23: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   from S23 have S24: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S25: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S26: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_lelttrt)
   from S25 S26 have S27: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_mp3an1)
   from S27 have S28: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S28 have S29: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_adantlr)
   from S18 S24 S29 have S30: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C \<ls> D ⟷ B⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S30 have S31: "(((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ B⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_biimpa)
   from S31 have S32: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ B⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_anasss)
   from S32 have S33: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ B⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_adantrrl)
   have S34: "A⋅C ∈ ℝ ∧ B⋅C ∈ ℝ ∧ B⋅D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C ∧ B⋅C \<ls> B⋅D ⟶ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_lelttrt)
   have S35: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S35 have S36: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2r)
   have S37: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S37 have S38: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantrr)
   from S38 have S39: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantll)
   have S40: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S40 have S41: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2l)
   from S34 S36 S39 S41 have S42: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C ∧ B⋅C \<ls> B⋅D ⟶ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_syl3anc)
   from S42 have S43: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅C ∧ B⋅C \<ls> B⋅D ⟶ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S17 S33 S43 have S44: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_mp2and)
   from S44 show "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<ls> B) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<ls> D ⟶ A⋅C \<ls> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_an4s)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemul12it: 
   shows "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅D"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S1 have S2: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2r)
   from S2 have S3: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S4 have S5: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S5 have S6: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_an42s)
   from S6 have S7: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S8 have S9: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2l)
   from S9 have S10: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ B⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S11: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> A⋅D" by (rule MMI_lemul2it)
   from S11 have S12: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> A⋅D" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S12 have S13: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> A⋅D" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S13 have S14: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> A⋅D" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   have S15: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   have S16: "𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ C \<lsq> D" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S14 S15 S16 have S17: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> A⋅D" by (rule MMI_syl2ani)
   from S17 have S18: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> A⋅D" by (rule MMI_adantlr)
   from S18 have S19: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> A⋅D" by (rule MMI_imp)
   have S20: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S20 have S21: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_a1i)
   have S22: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S23: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> D" by (rule MMI_letrt)
   from S22 S23 have S24: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> D" by (rule MMI_mp3an1)
   from S21 S24 have S25: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> D" by (rule MMI_im2anan9)
   have S26: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> D ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅D \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_lemul1it)
   from S26 have S27: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> D ∧ A \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅D \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S27 have S28: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅D \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_ancomsd)
   from S28 have S29: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅D \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S29 have S30: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅D \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_adantrl)
   from S25 S30 have S31: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅D \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_syld)
   from S31 have S32: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅D \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S3 S7 S10 S19 S32 have S33: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_letrd)
   from S33 show "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> B) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> C ∧ C \<lsq> D ⟶ A⋅C \<lsq> B⋅D" by (rule MMI_an4s)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_mulgt1t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_a1i)
   have S3: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   have S4: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S5: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S6: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭 ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_axlttrn)
   from S4 S5 S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭 ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_mp3an12)
   from S3 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_mpani)
   from S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S10: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S11: "(𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltmul2t)
   from S11 have S12: "(𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_biimpd)
   from S12 have S13: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S10 S13 have S14: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_mp3an1)
   from S14 have S15: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S9 S15 have S16: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_syld)
   from S16 have S17: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_imp3a)
   have S18: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S19: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_ax1id)
   from S18 S19 have S20: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S20 have S21: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S21 have S22: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B ⟷ A \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S17 S22 have S23: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ A \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylibd)
   from S2 S23 have S24: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ A \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_jcad)
   have S25: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   have S26: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S27: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ A⋅B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ A \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_axlttrn)
   from S26 S27 have S28: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A⋅B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ A \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_mp3an1)
   from S25 S28 have S29: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ A \<ls> A⋅B ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S24 S29 have S30: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_syld)
   from S30 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟭 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmulgt11t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> A⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S2: "(𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltmul2t)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_mp3anl1)
   from S3 have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_3impa)
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S7: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_ax1id)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S8 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant1)
   from S9 have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟭 \<ls> A⋅B ⟷ A \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S5 S10 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmulgt12t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B⋅A"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltmulgt11t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅B = B⋅A" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅B = B⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A⋅B = B⋅A" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A \<ls> A⋅B ⟷ A \<ls> B⋅A" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S7 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭 \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B⋅A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

 (*********** 431 - 440 **************************)

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemulge11t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> A⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℂ ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_ax1id)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S3 have S4: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A⋅𝟭 = A" by (rule MMI_ad2antrr)
   have S5: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> A) ∧ (𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> 𝟭 ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟭 \<lsq> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_lemul12it)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_2)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm2_43i)
   from S7 have S8: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ad2antrr)
   have S9: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S9 have S10: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_leidt)
   from S11 have S12: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_ad2antrr)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S8 S13 have S14: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   (A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ A \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_jca)
   have S15: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S15 have S16: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S17: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S16 S17 have S18: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_jctil)
   have S19: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 𝟭 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S19 have S20: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 𝟭 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   have S21: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S22: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S23: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   from S21 S22 S23 have S24: "𝟬 \<lsq> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_ltlei)
   from S20 S24 have S25: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> 𝟭 ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_jctil)
   from S18 S25 have S26: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   (𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> 𝟭 ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S5 S14 S26 have S27: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟭 \<lsq> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S4 S27 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟭 \<lsq> B ⟶ A \<lsq> A⋅B" by auto(*by (rule MMI_eqbrtrrd)*)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltdiv1t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B\<cdiv>C = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S6 S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S11: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S12: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   have S13: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S12 S13 have S14: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S14 have S15: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi2d)
   from S11 S15 have S16: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>C) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S17: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S17 have S18: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S19: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S19 have S20: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S21: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S21 have S22: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S18 S20 S22 have S23: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_ltdiv1)
   from S5 S10 S16 S23 have S24: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
   from S24 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lediv1t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B\<cdiv>C"
proof -
   have S1: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   B \<ls> A ⟷ B\<cdiv>C \<ls> A\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_ltdiv1t)
   from S1 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   B \<ls> A ⟷ B\<cdiv>C \<ls> A\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   B \<ls> A ⟷ B\<cdiv>C \<ls> A\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S3 have S4: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   B \<ls> A ⟷ B\<cdiv>C \<ls> A\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S4 have S5: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   ¬(B \<ls> A) ⟷ 
   ¬(B\<cdiv>C \<ls> A\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_negbid)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬(B \<ls> A)" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   from S6 have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬(B \<ls> A)" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S7 have S8: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬(B \<ls> A)" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S9: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S9 have S10: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantll)
   from S10 have S11: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_3adantl1)
   have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_redivclt)
   from S12 have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S13 have S14: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adantl2)
   have S15: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_redivclt)
   from S15 have S16: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S16 have S17: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adantl1)
   from S14 S17 have S18: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ ∧ B\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S11 S18 have S19: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ ∧ B\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   have S20: "A\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ ∧ B\<cdiv>C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B\<cdiv>C ⟷ 
   ¬(B\<cdiv>C \<ls> A\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   from S19 S20 have S21: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B\<cdiv>C ⟷ 
   ¬(B\<cdiv>C \<ls> A\<cdiv>C)" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S5 S8 S21 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_3bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_gt0divt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S2: "(𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_ltdiv1t)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_mp3anl1)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3impa)
   have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟬\<cdiv>B = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_div0t)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟬\<cdiv>B = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S5 S8 have S9: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬\<cdiv>B = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<ls> A\<cdiv>B ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S10 have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<ls> A\<cdiv>B ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S4 S11 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ge0divt: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   have S2: "(𝟬 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_lediv1t)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_mp3anl1)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3impa)
   have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟬\<cdiv>B = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_div0t)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟬\<cdiv>B = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S5 S8 have S9: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬\<cdiv>B = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S10 have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬\<cdiv>B \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S4 S11 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divgt0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_gt0divt)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_biimpd)
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3exp)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_com34)
   from S4 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_imp43)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divge0t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   have S1: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_ge0divt)
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_biimpd)
   from S2 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3exp)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_com34)
   from S4 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_imp43)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divgt0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_divgt0t)
   from S1 S2 S3 show "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_mpanl12)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divge0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_divge0t)
   from S1 S2 S3 show "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<lsq> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_mpanl12)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divgt0i2: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "𝟬 \<ls> B"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   from A3 have S1: "𝟬 \<ls> B".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S3: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S2 S3 have S4: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_divgt0)
   from S1 S4 show "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_mpan2)
qed
