lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_divgt0i: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "𝟬 \<ls> A" and
    A4: "𝟬 \<ls> B"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   from A3 have S1: "𝟬 \<ls> A".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S3: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A4 have S4: "𝟬 \<ls> B".
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_divgt0i2)
   from S1 S5 show "𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recgt0t: 
   shows "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   have S2: "𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭" by (rule MMI_lt01)
   have S3: "(𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭 ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_divgt0t)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "(𝟭 ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_mpanr1)
   from S1 S4 show "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_mpanl1)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_recgt0: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_recgt0t)
   from S1 S2 show "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_mpan)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmuldivt: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> C\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B \<ls> C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ls> C\<cdiv>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> C\<cdiv>B) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> C\<cdiv>B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S6: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S7: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S7 have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S8 S10 have S11: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>B) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S6 S11 have S12: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S13: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S14: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) = ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq1)
   from S14 have S15: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S13 S15 have S16: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S16 have S17: "C =  if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> C ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> C\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi2d)
   have S18: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S18 have S19: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S20: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S20 have S21: " if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S22: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S22 have S23: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S19 S21 S23 have S24: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(C ∈ ℝ, C, 𝟬))\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_ltmuldiv)
   from S5 S12 S17 S24 have S25: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_dedth3h)
   from S25 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltmuldiv2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅A = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅A = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S4 have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅A = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S5 have S6: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ B⋅A = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S6 have S7: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   B⋅A \<ls> C ⟷ A⋅B \<ls> C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S8: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   B⋅A \<ls> C ⟷ B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_ltmuldivt)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_bitr3d)
   from S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S10 have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S11 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C ⟷ B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltdivmult: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> B⋅C"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B⋅C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> B⋅C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_ltdiv1t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp1)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp2)
   from S2 S4 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ B⋅C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   from S1 S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> B⋅C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S8 have S9: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S11: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_divcan3t)
   from S11 have S12: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_3exp)
   from S12 have S13: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_imp)
   have S14: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S15: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S13 S14 S15 have S16: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S10 S16 have S17: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_syld)
   from S17 have S18: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S18 have S19: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S19 have S20: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> B⋅C\<cdiv>B ⟷ A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 S20 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_bitr2d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ledivmult: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ A \<lsq> B⋅C"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B⋅C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B⋅C ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> B⋅C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_lediv1t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp1)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp2)
   from S2 S4 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ B⋅C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   from S1 S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B⋅C ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> B⋅C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S8 have S9: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S11: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_divcan3t)
   from S11 have S12: "B ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_3exp)
   from S12 have S13: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_imp)
   have S14: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S15: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S13 S14 S15 have S16: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S10 S16 have S17: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_syld)
   from S17 have S18: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S18 have S19: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B⋅C\<cdiv>B = C" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S19 have S20: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> B⋅C\<cdiv>B ⟷ A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S7 S20 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ A \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_bitr2d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltdivmul2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> C⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_ltdivmult)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S7 have S8: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B⋅C ⟷ A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S8 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lt2mul2divt: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C⋅D ⟷ A\<cdiv>D \<ls> C\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   have S1: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ D ∈ ℂ ⟶ C⋅D = D⋅C" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S2: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S3: "D ∈ ℝ ⟶ D ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ C⋅D = D⋅C" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S4 have S5: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C⋅D\<cdiv>B = D⋅C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_opreq1d)
   from S5 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C⋅D\<cdiv>B = D⋅C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant2)
   have S7: "(D ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   D⋅C\<cdiv>B = D⋅(C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_divasst)
   from S3 have S8: "D ∈ ℝ ⟶ D ∈ ℂ" .
   from S8 have S9: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ D ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_ad2antlr)
   from S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ D ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S2 have S11: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" .
   from S11 have S12: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_ad2antrl)
   from S12 have S13: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S14: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S14 have S15: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant1)
   from S10 S13 S15 have S16: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   D ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   have S17: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S17 have S18: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   from S7 S16 S18 have S19: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   D⋅C\<cdiv>B = D⋅(C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S6 S19 have S20: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C⋅D\<cdiv>B = D⋅(C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_eqtrd)
   from S20 have S21: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   C⋅D\<cdiv>B = D⋅(C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_3adant3r)
   from S21 have S22: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   C⋅D\<cdiv>B = D⋅(C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_3adant1l)
   from S22 have S23: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A \<ls> C⋅D\<cdiv>B ⟷ A \<ls> D⋅(C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   have S24: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C⋅D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C⋅D ⟷ A \<ls> C⋅D\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_ltmuldivt)
   have S25: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S25 have S26: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant1)
   have S27: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S27 have S28: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant1)
   have S29: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ C⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S29 have S30: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ C⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant2)
   from S26 S28 S30 have S31: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C⋅D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   have S32: "𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S32 have S33: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant3)
   from S24 S31 S33 have S34: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C⋅D ⟷ A \<ls> C⋅D\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S35: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>D \<ls> C\<cdiv>B ⟷ A \<ls> D⋅(C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_ltdivmult)
   from S26 have S36: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" .
   have S37: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ⟶ D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S37 have S38: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant2)
   have S39: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_redivclt)
   have S40: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp1)
   have S41: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp2)
   from S17 have S42: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S42 have S43: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S39 S40 S41 S43 have S44: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syl3anc)
   from S44 have S45: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S45 have S46: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant3r)
   from S46 have S47: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant2r)
   from S47 have S48: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant1l)
   from S36 S38 S48 have S49: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   have S50: "𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> D" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S50 have S51: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> D" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant3)
   from S35 S49 S51 have S52: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>D \<ls> C\<cdiv>B ⟷ A \<ls> D⋅(C\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S23 S34 S52 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<ls> C⋅D ⟷ A\<cdiv>D \<ls> C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ledivmul2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ A \<lsq> C⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ A \<lsq> B⋅C" by (rule MMI_ledivmult)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S4: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S2 S3 S4 have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B⋅C = C⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S7 have S8: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B⋅C ⟷ A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S8 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

(************ 451 -460 *************************)



lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemuldivt: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ A \<lsq> C\<cdiv>B"
proof -
   have S1: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<ls> A ⟷ C \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltdivmul2t)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟷ 
   C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3anrev)
   from S1 S2 have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<ls> A ⟷ C \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylanb)
   from S3 have S4: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ¬(C\<cdiv>B \<ls> A) ⟷ ¬(C \<ls> A⋅B)" by (rule MMI_negbid)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> C\<cdiv>B ⟷ ¬(C\<cdiv>B \<ls> A)" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp1)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S8 have S9: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantlr)
   have S10: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_redivclt)
   from S10 have S11: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S11 have S12: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S9 S12 have S13: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S13 have S14: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ C\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adantl1)
   from S5 S7 S14 have S15: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> C\<cdiv>B ⟷ ¬(C\<cdiv>B \<ls> A)" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S16: "A⋅B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ ¬(C \<ls> A⋅B)" by (rule MMI_lenltt)
   have S17: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S17 have S18: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S19: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp3)
   from S16 S18 S19 have S20: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ ¬(C \<ls> A⋅B)" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S20 have S21: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ ¬(C \<ls> A⋅B)" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S4 S15 S21 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ A \<lsq> C\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_3bitr4rd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lemuldiv2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ⟶ B⋅A = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_axmulcom)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅A = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S4 have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B⋅A = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S5 have S6: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ B⋅A = A⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S6 have S7: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   B⋅A \<lsq> C ⟷ A⋅B \<lsq> C" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S8: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   B⋅A \<lsq> C ⟷ B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_lemuldivt)
   from S7 S8 have S9: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_bitr3d)
   from S9 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S10 have S11: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S11 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A⋅B \<lsq> C ⟷ B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltreci: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "𝟬 \<ls> A" and
    A4: "𝟬 \<ls> B"   
   shows "A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 have S2: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A1 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S4: "𝟬 \<ls> A".
   from S3 S4 have S5: "A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0i)
   from S2 S5 have S6: "A\<cdiv>A = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_divid)
   from A2 have S7: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S7 have S8: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A2 have S9: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A4 have S10: "𝟬 \<ls> B".
   from S9 S10 have S11: "B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0i)
   from S8 S11 have S12: "B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) = 𝟭" by (rule MMI_recid)
   from S6 S12 have S13: "A\<cdiv>A = B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_eqtr4)
   from S8 have S14: "B ∈ ℂ" .
   from S2 have S15: "A ∈ ℂ" .
   from S5 have S16: "A ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S14 S15 S16 have S17: "B\<cdiv>A = B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_divrec)
   from S13 S17 have S18: "A\<cdiv>A \<ls> B\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_breq12i)
   from A1 have S19: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S20: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S21: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S22: "𝟬 \<ls> A".
   from S19 S20 S21 S22 have S23: "A \<ls> B ⟷ A\<cdiv>A \<ls> B\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_ltdiv1i)
   from A4 have S24: "𝟬 \<ls> B".
   from A2 have S25: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S11 have S26: "B ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S25 S26 have S27: "𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rereccl)
   from A1 have S28: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S5 have S29: "A ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S28 S29 have S30: "𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rereccl)
   from A2 have S31: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S27 S30 S31 have S32: "𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_ltmul2)
   from S24 S32 have S33: "𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> B⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_ax_mp)
   from S18 S23 S33 show "A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3bitr4)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltrec: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭)) \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S2: "A =  if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A = 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S2 have S3: "A =  if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S1 S3 have S4: "A =  if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   (A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A) ⟷ 
   ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   have S5: "B =  if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭)) \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S6: "B =  if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S6 have S7: "B =  if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭)) \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S5 S7 have S8: "B =  if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭) ⟶ 
   (( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))) ⟷ 
   ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭)) \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭)) \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from A1 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ".
   have S10: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S9 S10 have S11: " if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   from A2 have S12: "B ∈ ℝ".
   have S13: "𝟭 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ax1re)
   from S12 S13 have S14: " if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_keepel)
   have S15: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_elimgt0)
   have S16: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_elimgt0)
   from S11 S14 S15 S16 have S17: "( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭)) \<ls> ( if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> B, B, 𝟭)) \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(𝟬 \<ls> A, A, 𝟭))" by (rule MMI_ltreci)
   from S4 S8 S17 show "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lerec: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_ltrec)
   from A1 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S4 have S5: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S6 have S7: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S5 S7 have S8: "A ≠ 𝟬 ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A = 𝟭\<cdiv>B ⟷ A = B" by (rule MMI_rec11)
   from A1 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S9 have S10: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0)
   from A2 have S11: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S11 have S12: "𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0)
   from S8 S10 S12 have S13: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A = 𝟭\<cdiv>B ⟷ A = B" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   have S14: "𝟭\<cdiv>A = 𝟭\<cdiv>B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_eqcom)
   from S13 S14 have S15: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A = B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_syl5rbbr)
   from S3 S15 have S16: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∨ 𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_orbi12d)
   from S12 have S17: "𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" .
   from A2 have S18: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S18 have S19: "B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rerecclz)
   from S17 S19 have S20: "𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S10 have S21: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" .
   from A1 have S22: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S22 have S23: "A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rerecclz)
   from S21 S23 have S24: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S20 S24 have S25: "𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_anim12i)
   from S25 have S26: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   have S27: "𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∨ 𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_leloet)
   from S26 S27 have S28: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∨ 𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_syl)
   from S16 S28 have S29: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ∨ A = B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
   from A1 have S30: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S31: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S30 S31 have S32: "A \<lsq> B ⟷ A \<ls> B ∨ A = B" by (rule MMI_leloe)
   from S29 S32 show "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_syl5bb)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lt2msq: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S3: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> A⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltmul2)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S7: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S5 S6 S7 have S8: "𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅B \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltmul1)
   from S4 S8 have S9: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ∧ A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   A⋅A \<ls> A⋅B ∧ A⋅B \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_bi2anan9)
   have S10: "A \<ls> B ∧ A \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_anidm)
   from S9 S10 have S11: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   A⋅A \<ls> A⋅B ∧ A⋅B \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl5bbr)
   from A1 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S13: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S12 S13 have S14: "A⋅A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A1 have S15: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S16: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S15 S16 have S17: "A⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A2 have S18: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S19: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S18 S19 have S20: "B⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from S14 S17 S20 have S21: "A⋅A \<ls> A⋅B ∧ A⋅B \<ls> B⋅B ⟶ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_lttr)
   from S11 S21 have S22: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟶ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl6bi)
   from A2 have S23: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S24: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S25: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S23 S24 S25 have S26: "𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B \<lsq> A ⟷ B⋅B \<lsq> B⋅A" by (rule MMI_lemul2)
   from A2 have S27: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S28: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S29: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S27 S28 S29 have S30: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   B \<lsq> A ⟷ B⋅A \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_lemul1)
   from S26 S30 have S31: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B \<lsq> A ∧ B \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   B⋅B \<lsq> B⋅A ∧ B⋅A \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_bi2anan9r)
   have S32: "B \<lsq> A ∧ B \<lsq> A ⟷ B \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_anidm)
   from S31 S32 have S33: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   B⋅B \<lsq> B⋅A ∧ B⋅A \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl5bbr)
   from S20 have S34: "B⋅B ∈ ℝ" .
   from A2 have S35: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S36: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S35 S36 have S37: "B⋅A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from S14 have S38: "A⋅A ∈ ℝ" .
   from S34 S37 S38 have S39: "B⋅B \<lsq> B⋅A ∧ B⋅A \<lsq> A⋅A ⟶ B⋅B \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_letr)
   from S33 S39 have S40: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B \<lsq> A ⟶ B⋅B \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl6bi)
   from A2 have S41: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S42: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S41 S42 have S43: "B \<lsq> A ⟷ ¬(A \<ls> B)" by (rule MMI_lenlt)
   from S20 have S44: "B⋅B ∈ ℝ" .
   from S14 have S45: "A⋅A ∈ ℝ" .
   from S44 S45 have S46: "B⋅B \<lsq> A⋅A ⟷ 
   ¬(A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B)" by (rule MMI_lenlt)
   from S40 S43 S46 have S47: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ¬(A \<ls> B) ⟶ 
   ¬(A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B)" by (rule MMI_3imtr3g)
   from S47 have S48: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B ⟶ A \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_a3d)
   from S22 S48 have S49: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_impbid)
   have S50: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S50 have S51: "𝟬 = A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S52: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A2 have S53: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S54: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S52 S53 S54 have S55: "𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   B⋅𝟬 \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltmul2)
   have S56: "𝟬 = A ⟶ A⋅𝟬 = A⋅A" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S56 have S57: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟬 \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from A2 have S58: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S58 have S59: "B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S59 have S60: "B⋅𝟬 = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul01)
   from A1 have S61: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S61 have S62: "A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recn)
   from S62 have S63: "A⋅𝟬 = 𝟬" by (rule MMI_mul01)
   from S60 S63 have S64: "B⋅𝟬 = A⋅𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqtr4)
   from S64 have S65: "B⋅𝟬 \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ 
   A⋅𝟬 \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq1i)
   from S57 S65 have S66: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   B⋅𝟬 \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl5bb)
   from S55 S66 have S67: "𝟬 = A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylan9bbr)
   from S51 S67 have S68: "𝟬 = A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_bitr3d)
   have S69: "𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ B \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S69 have S70: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ B \<lsq> A" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   have S71: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A1 have S72: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S73: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S71 S72 S73 have S74: "𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   A⋅𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_lemul2)
   have S75: "𝟬 = B ⟶ B⋅𝟬 = B⋅B" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S75 have S76: "𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   B⋅𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅A ⟷ B⋅B \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S63 have S77: "A⋅𝟬 = 𝟬" .
   from S60 have S78: "B⋅𝟬 = 𝟬" .
   from S77 S78 have S79: "A⋅𝟬 = B⋅𝟬" by (rule MMI_eqtr4)
   from S79 have S80: "A⋅𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅A ⟷ 
   B⋅𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_breq1i)
   from S76 S80 have S81: "𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   A⋅𝟬 \<lsq> A⋅A ⟷ B⋅B \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_syl5bb)
   from S74 S81 have S82: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ B⋅B \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_sylan9bb)
   from S70 S82 have S83: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   B \<lsq> A ⟷ B⋅B \<lsq> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_bitr3d)
   from S43 have S84: "B \<lsq> A ⟷ ¬(A \<ls> B)" .
   from S46 have S85: "B⋅B \<lsq> A⋅A ⟷ 
   ¬(A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B)" .
   from S83 S84 S85 have S86: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   ¬(A \<ls> B) ⟷ 
   ¬(A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B)" by (rule MMI_3bitr3g)
   from S86 have S87: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_con4bid)
   have S88: "¬(A \<ls> B) ∧ ¬(A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B) ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_pm5_21)
   from A2 have S89: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S89 have S90: "¬(B \<ls> B)" by (rule MMI_ltnr)
   have S91: "𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ B \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   from S91 have S92: "𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   B \<ls> B ⟷ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_bicomd)
   from S50 have S93: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B" .
   from S92 S93 have S94: "𝟬 = A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   B \<ls> B ⟷ A \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_sylan9bbr)
   from S90 S94 have S95: "𝟬 = A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ ¬(A \<ls> B)" by (rule MMI_mtbii)
   from S20 have S96: "B⋅B ∈ ℝ" .
   from S96 have S97: "¬(B⋅B \<ls> B⋅B)" by (rule MMI_ltnr)
   from S75 have S98: "𝟬 = B ⟶ B⋅𝟬 = B⋅B" .
   from S98 have S99: "𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   B⋅𝟬 \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ B⋅B \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S99 have S100: "𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   B⋅B \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ 
   B⋅𝟬 \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_bicomd)
   from S66 have S101: "𝟬 = A ⟶ 
   B⋅𝟬 \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" .
   from S100 S101 have S102: "𝟬 = A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   B⋅B \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylan9bbr)
   from S97 S102 have S103: "𝟬 = A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   ¬(A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B)" by (rule MMI_mtbii)
   from S88 S95 S103 have S104: "𝟬 = A ∧ 𝟬 = B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S49 S68 S87 S104 have S105: "(𝟬 \<ls> A ∨ 𝟬 = A) ∧ (𝟬 \<ls> B ∨ 𝟬 = B) ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_ccase)
   have S106: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A1 have S107: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S106 S107 have S108: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∨ 𝟬 = A" by (rule MMI_leloe)
   have S109: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from A2 have S110: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S109 S110 have S111: "𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ∨ 𝟬 = B" by (rule MMI_leloe)
   from S105 S108 S111 show "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_syl2anb)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_le2msq: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅A \<lsq> B⋅B"
proof -
   from A2 have S1: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S2: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟶ 
   B \<ls> A ⟷ B⋅B \<ls> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_lt2msq)
   from S3 have S4: "𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟶ 
   ¬(B \<ls> A) ⟷ 
   ¬(B⋅B \<ls> A⋅A)" by (rule MMI_negbid)
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S5 S6 have S7: "A \<lsq> B ⟷ ¬(B \<ls> A)" by (rule MMI_lenlt)
   from A1 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S8 S9 have S10: "A⋅A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A2 have S11: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S12: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S11 S12 have S13: "B⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from S10 S13 have S14: "A⋅A \<lsq> B⋅B ⟷ 
   ¬(B⋅B \<ls> A⋅A)" by (rule MMI_lenlt)
   from S4 S7 S14 have S15: "𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅A \<lsq> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_3bitr4g)
   from S15 show "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ A⋅A \<lsq> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_msq11: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A⋅A = B⋅B ⟷ A = B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 S2 have S3: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_lt2msq)
   from A2 have S4: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S5: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S4 S5 have S6: "𝟬 \<lsq> B ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟶ 
   B \<ls> A ⟷ B⋅B \<ls> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_lt2msq)
   from S6 have S7: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   B \<ls> A ⟷ B⋅B \<ls> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S3 S7 have S8: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A ⟷ 
   A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B ∨ B⋅B \<ls> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_orbi12d)
   from A1 have S9: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S10: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S9 S10 have S11: "¬(A = B) ⟷ A \<ls> B ∨ B \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_lttri2)
   from A1 have S12: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A1 have S13: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from S12 S13 have S14: "A⋅A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from A2 have S15: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S16: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from S15 S16 have S17: "B⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_remulcl)
   from S14 S17 have S18: "¬(A⋅A = B⋅B) ⟷ 
   A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B ∨ B⋅B \<ls> A⋅A" by (rule MMI_lttri2)
   from S8 S11 S18 have S19: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   ¬(A = B) ⟷ ¬(A⋅A = B⋅B)" by (rule MMI_3bitr4g)
   from S19 have S20: "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A = B ⟷ A⋅A = B⋅B" by (rule MMI_con4bid)
   from S20 show "𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A⋅A = B⋅B ⟷ A = B" by (rule MMI_bicomd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltrect: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A = 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S3 S5 have S6: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S2 S6 have S7: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S11: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S11 have S12: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S9 S13 have S14: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S15: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S15 have S16: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S17: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S17 have S18: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S16 S18 have S19: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_ltrec)
   from S7 S14 S19 have S20: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S20 have S21: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S21 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_an4s)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lerect: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A = 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S3 S5 have S6: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S2 S6 have S7: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S11: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S11 have S12: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S9 S13 have S14: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S15: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S15 have S16: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S17: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S17 have S18: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S16 S18 have S19: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_lerec)
   from S7 S14 S19 have S20: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S20 have S21: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S21 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_an4s)
qed

 (************* 461 - 470 **************************)

 lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lerectOLD: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A = 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S3 S5 have S6: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S2 S6 have S7: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S8: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S8 have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S11: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B = 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq2)
   from S11 have S12: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S9 S13 have S14: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S15: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S15 have S16: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S17: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S17 have S18: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S16 S18 have S19: "𝟬 \<ls> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_lerec)
   from S7 S14 S19 have S20: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S20 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_imp)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lt2msqt: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B"
proof -
   have S1: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S1 have S2: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_anbi1d)
   have S3: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_breq1)
   have S4: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∧ A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅A = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq12)
   from S4 have S5: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅A = ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anidms)
   from S5 have S6: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S3 S6 have S7: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S2 S7 have S8: "A =  if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B⋅B)" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S9: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   from S9 have S10: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anbi2d)
   have S11: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2)
   have S12: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∧ B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B⋅B = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_opreq12)
   from S12 have S13: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   B⋅B = ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_anidms)
   from S13 have S14: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B⋅B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S11 S14 have S15: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B⋅B) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_bibi12d)
   from S10 S15 have S16: "B =  if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ⟶ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> B⋅B) ⟷ 
   (𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)))" by (rule MMI_imbi12d)
   have S17: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S17 have S18: " if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   have S19: "𝟬 ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_0re)
   from S19 have S20: " if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬) ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_elimel)
   from S18 S20 have S21: "𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟶ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬)) ⟷ 
   ( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬))⋅( if(A ∈ ℝ, A, 𝟬)) \<ls> ( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))⋅( if(B ∈ ℝ, B, 𝟬))" by (rule MMI_lt2msq)
   from S8 S16 S21 have S22: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_dedth2h)
   from S22 have S23: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_imp)
   from S23 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<lsq> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ A⋅A \<ls> B⋅B" by (rule MMI_an4s)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltdiv2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟷ 
   (A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C" by (rule MMI_an6)
   have S2: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_ltrect)
   from S2 have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S4: "(𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_ltmul2t)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rerecclt)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "(𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_syl3anl2)
   have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rerecclt)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "((B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_syl3anl1)
   have S9: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_divrect)
   have S10: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S9 S10 have S11: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_syl3an2)
   from S11 have S12: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_3expb)
   from S12 have S13: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S14: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>A = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_divrect)
   have S15: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S14 S15 have S16: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>A = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_syl3an2)
   from S16 have S17: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>A = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_3expb)
   from S17 have S18: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>A = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   from S13 S18 have S19: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S19 have S20: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℂ ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_3coml)
   have S21: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S20 S21 have S22: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_syl3an3)
   from S22 have S23: "((B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<ls> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S8 S23 have S24: "((B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_bitr4d)
   from S24 have S25: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_ex)
   from S25 have S26: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S26 have S27: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3exp)
   from S27 have S28: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_imp4a)
   from S28 have S29: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3imp)
   have S30: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   have S31: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S30 S31 have S32: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S29 S32 have S33: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_syl3an2)
   have S34: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   have S35: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S34 S35 have S36: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S33 S36 have S37: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_syl3an1)
   from S3 S37 have S38: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
   from S1 S38 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> B ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<ls> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_sylbi)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltrec1t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> B ⟷ 𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> A"
proof -
   have S1: "(𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_ltrect)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rerecclt)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   have S5: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_recgt0t)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2r)
   have S8: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_id)
   from S8 have S9: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2l)
   from S1 S7 S9 have S10: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S11: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>A) = A" by (rule MMI_recrect)
   have S12: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S12 have S13: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S2 have S14: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S11 S13 S14 have S15: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>A) = A" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S15 have S16: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>A) = A" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2r)
   from S16 have S17: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>A) ⟷ 𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S10 S17 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>A \<ls> B ⟷ 𝟭\<cdiv>B \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lerec2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>B ⟷ B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_lerectOLD)
   have S2: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S2 have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rerecclt)
   from S4 S5 have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2l)
   from S3 S7 have S8: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_jca)
   have S9: "𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S9 have S10: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A" by (rule MMI_adantl)
   have S11: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_recgt0t)
   from S11 have S12: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2l)
   from S10 S12 have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> 𝟭\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S1 S8 S13 have S14: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S15: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>B) = B" by (rule MMI_recrect)
   have S16: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S16 have S17: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S4 have S18: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S15 S17 S18 have S19: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>B) = B" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S19 have S20: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>B) = B" by (rule MMI_ad2ant2l)
   from S20 have S21: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   from S14 S21 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>B ⟷ B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ledivdivt: 
   shows "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>D ⟷ D\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "(A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ C\<cdiv>D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C\<cdiv>D ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>D ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(C\<cdiv>D) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>(A\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_lerectOLD)
   from S1 have S2: "(A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B) ∧ C\<cdiv>D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C\<cdiv>D ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>D ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(C\<cdiv>D) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>(A\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_an4s)
   have S3: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_redivclt)
   from S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3expb)
   have S5: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   have S6: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S5 S6 have S7: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S4 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_sylan2)
   from S8 have S9: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantlr)
   have S10: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_divgt0t)
   from S10 have S11: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_an4s)
   from S9 S11 have S12: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A\<cdiv>B" by (rule MMI_jca)
   have S13: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ D ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C\<cdiv>D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_redivclt)
   from S13 have S14: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ D ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C\<cdiv>D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3expb)
   have S15: "D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   have S16: "D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ D ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S15 S16 have S17: "D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   D ∈ ℝ ∧ D ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S14 S17 have S18: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ C\<cdiv>D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_sylan2)
   from S18 have S19: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ C\<cdiv>D ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantlr)
   have S20: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ D ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> C\<cdiv>D" by (rule MMI_divgt0t)
   from S20 have S21: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> C\<cdiv>D" by (rule MMI_an4s)
   from S19 S21 have S22: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C\<cdiv>D" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S2 S12 S22 have S23: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>D ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(C\<cdiv>D) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>(A\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   have S24: "(C ∈ ℂ ∧ D ∈ ℂ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ∧ D ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(C\<cdiv>D) = D\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_recdivt)
   from S24 have S25: "(C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬) ∧ D ∈ ℂ ∧ D ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(C\<cdiv>D) = D\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_an4s)
   have S26: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S26 have S27: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S28: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S27 S28 have S29: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   C ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   have S30: "D ∈ ℝ ⟶ D ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S30 have S31: "D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ D ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S16 have S32: "D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ D ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S31 S32 have S33: "D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   D ∈ ℂ ∧ D ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S25 S29 S33 have S34: "(C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(C\<cdiv>D) = D\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   have S35: "(A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ) ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(A\<cdiv>B) = B\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_recdivt)
   from S35 have S36: "(A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬) ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(A\<cdiv>B) = B\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_an4s)
   have S37: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S37 have S38: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S39: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S38 S39 have S40: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   have S41: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S41 have S42: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S6 have S43: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S42 S43 have S44: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S36 S40 S44 have S45: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(A\<cdiv>B) = B\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S34 S45 have S46: "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>(C\<cdiv>D) \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>(A\<cdiv>B) ⟷ D\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_breqan12rd)
   from S23 S46 show "((A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ (C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C) ∧ D ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> D ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>D ⟷ D\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lediv2t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A"
proof -
   have S1: "(𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<lsq> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_lemul2t)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   have S3: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rerecclt)
   from S2 S3 have S4: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S4 have S5: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant2)
   have S6: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   have S7: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_rerecclt)
   from S6 S7 have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S8 have S9: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant1)
   have S10: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_pm3_26)
   from S10 have S11: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant3)
   from S5 S9 S11 have S12: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟭\<cdiv>A ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   have S13: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> C" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S13 have S14: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> C" by (rule MMI_3ad2ant3)
   from S1 S12 S14 have S15: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<lsq> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   have S16: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_lerectOLD)
   from S16 have S17: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_an4s)
   from S17 have S18: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ 
   𝟭\<cdiv>B \<lsq> 𝟭\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   have S19: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_divrect)
   from S19 have S20: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_3expb)
   have S21: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S22: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S22 have S23: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S2 have S24: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S23 S24 have S25: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S20 S21 S25 have S26: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S26 have S27: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B)" by (rule MMI_3adant2)
   have S28: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>A = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_divrect)
   from S28 have S29: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>A = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_3expb)
   from S21 have S30: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" .
   have S31: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S31 have S32: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S6 have S33: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ A ≠ 𝟬" .
   from S32 S33 have S34: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℂ ∧ A ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_jca)
   from S29 S30 S34 have S35: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>A = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_syl2an)
   from S35 have S36: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>A = C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_3adant3)
   from S27 S36 have S37: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ (A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<lsq> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_breq12d)
   from S37 have S38: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<lsq> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_3coml)
   from S38 have S39: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   C\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A ⟷ 
   C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>B) \<lsq> C⋅(𝟭\<cdiv>A)" by (rule MMI_3adant3r)
   from S15 S18 S39 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> A) ∧ (B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B) ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> B ⟷ C\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C\<cdiv>A" by (rule MMI_3bitr4d)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltdiv23t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B"
proof -
   have S1: "(A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_ltmul1t)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S2 have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantll)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_redivclt)
   from S4 have S5: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S3 S5 have S6: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adantl3)
   have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp3)
   from S8 have S9: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp2)
   from S10 have S11: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S7 S9 S11 have S12: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S1 S12 S13 have S14: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S14 have S15: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ 
   (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantrr)
   from S3 have S16: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" .
   have S17: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_divcan1t)
   from S17 have S18: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S18 have S19: "(A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   have S20: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S21: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S20 S21 have S22: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_anim12i)
   from S19 S22 have S23: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S16 S23 have S24: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S24 have S25: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_3adantl3)
   from S25 have S26: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_adantrr)
   from S26 have S27: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B \<ls> C⋅B ⟷ A \<ls> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S28: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ C⋅B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> C⋅B ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<ls> C⋅B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_ltdiv1t)
   have S29: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp1)
   have S30: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ C⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S30 have S31: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S31 have S32: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S8 have S33: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" .
   from S29 S32 S33 have S34: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ C⋅B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   from S28 S34 have S35: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> C⋅B ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<ls> C⋅B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   have S36: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S36 have S37: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantll)
   have S38: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_divcan3t)
   from S21 have S39: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" .
   from S38 S39 have S40: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_syl3an2)
   have S41: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S40 S41 have S42: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_syl3an1)
   from S42 have S43: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S43 have S44: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S37 S44 have S45: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S45 have S46: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_3adantl1)
   from S46 have S47: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<ls> C⋅B\<cdiv>C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S35 S47 have S48: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> C⋅B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
   from S48 have S49: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<ls> C⋅B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_adantrl)
   from S15 S27 S49 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_3bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_lediv23t: 
   shows "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B"
proof -
   have S1: "(A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ 
   (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_lemul1t)
   have S2: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S2 have S3: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantll)
   have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_redivclt)
   from S4 have S5: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S3 S5 have S6: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S6 have S7: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adantl3)
   have S8: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp3)
   from S8 have S9: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   have S10: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp2)
   from S10 have S11: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_adantr)
   from S7 S9 S11 have S12: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   have S13: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 𝟬 \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_pm3_27)
   from S1 S12 S13 have S14: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ 
   (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_sylanc)
   from S14 have S15: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ 
   (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_adantrr)
   from S3 have S16: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ B ≠ 𝟬" .
   have S17: "B ∈ ℂ ∧ A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_divcan1t)
   from S17 have S18: "A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S18 have S19: "(A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   have S20: "A ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   have S21: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S20 S21 have S22: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_anim12i)
   from S19 S22 have S23: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ B ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   from S16 S23 have S24: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S24 have S25: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_3adantl3)
   from S25 have S26: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B = A" by (rule MMI_adantrr)
   from S26 have S27: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   (A\<cdiv>B)⋅B \<lsq> C⋅B ⟷ A \<lsq> C⋅B" by (rule MMI_breq1d)
   have S28: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ C⋅B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> C⋅B ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> C⋅B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_lediv1t)
   have S29: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ A ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3simp1)
   have S30: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ⟶ C⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_axmulrcl)
   from S30 have S31: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_ancoms)
   from S31 have S32: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C⋅B ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3adant1)
   from S8 have S33: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℝ" .
   from S29 S32 S33 have S34: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ⟶ 
   A ∈ ℝ ∧ C⋅B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3jca)
   from S28 S34 have S35: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> C⋅B ⟷ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> C⋅B\<cdiv>C" by (rule MMI_sylan)
   have S36: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_gt0ne0t)
   from S36 have S37: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C ≠ 𝟬" by (rule MMI_adantll)
   have S38: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℂ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_divcan3t)
   from S21 have S39: "B ∈ ℝ ⟶ B ∈ ℂ" .
   from S38 S39 have S40: "C ∈ ℂ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_syl3an2)
   have S41: "C ∈ ℝ ⟶ C ∈ ℂ" by (rule MMI_recnt)
   from S40 S41 have S42: "C ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_syl3an1)
   from S42 have S43: "B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_3com12)
   from S43 have S44: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ C ≠ 𝟬 ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_3expa)
   from S37 S44 have S45: "(B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_syldan)
   from S45 have S46: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ C⋅B\<cdiv>C = B" by (rule MMI_3adantl1)
   from S46 have S47: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> C⋅B\<cdiv>C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_breq2d)
   from S35 S47 have S48: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> C⋅B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_bitrd)
   from S48 have S49: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A \<lsq> C⋅B ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_adantrl)
   from S15 S27 S49 show "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<lsq> C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<lsq> B" by (rule MMI_3bitrd)
qed

lemma (in MMIsar0) MMI_ltdiv23: assumes A1: "A ∈ ℝ" and
    A2: "B ∈ ℝ" and
    A3: "C ∈ ℝ"   
   shows "𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B"
proof -
   from A1 have S1: "A ∈ ℝ".
   from A2 have S2: "B ∈ ℝ".
   from A3 have S3: "C ∈ ℝ".
   from S1 S2 S3 have S4: "A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ" by (rule MMI_3pm3_2i)
   have S5: "(A ∈ ℝ ∧ B ∈ ℝ ∧ C ∈ ℝ) ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_ltdiv23t)
   from S4 S5 show "𝟬 \<ls> B ∧ 𝟬 \<ls> C ⟶ 
   A\<cdiv>B \<ls> C ⟷ A\<cdiv>C \<ls> B" by (rule MMI_mpan)
qed
